NK071(du)005:1: // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam rnam par bshad pa chung
NK071(du)005:2: ngu'i 'bru 'grel bdud rtsi'i thigs pa zhes bya ba
NK071(du)005:4: gdod ma'i mgon po gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK071(du)005:5: dbyer med slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba la //
NK071(du)005:6: sgo gsum gus pa chen pos phyag 'tshal te //
NK071(du)005:7: sgyu 'phrul lam chung 'bru 'grel bri bar bya //
NK071(du)005:8: de la 'dir tan+t+ra chen po bco brgyad kyi gazhi'am
NK071(du)005:9: snying po dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sems dang ye
NK071(du)005:10: shes rang snang du sangs rgyas pa'i gsang ba chen
NK071(du)005:11: po chos kun gyi snying po sku gsum 'du 'bral
NK071(du)005:12: med pa'i de kho na nyid skal ba dang ldan
NK071(du)005:13: pa la gzhi lam 'bras bu dbyer med du nges
NK071(du)005:14: pa tshe 'dir mngon sangs rgyas par 'dod pa rnams
NK071(du)005:15: kyis ye nas chos kun dag mnyam chen po mngon
NK071(du)005:16: du bya ba la nyams su len bya lam rnam
NK071(du)005:20: mtha' mar dge ba'i sa bcad gsum las /
NK071(du)005:30: nges don sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i go 'phang mngon du
NK071(du)005:31: bya ba 'i lam rnam para nges pa'i bshad pa
NK071(du)005:32: rgyud kyi dgongs don tshig tshogs nyung ngur bsdus pas
NK071(du)005:33: chung ngu'am tshegs chung ngus don chen po 'grub pa
NK071(du)005:34: la man ngag ces grags pa ltar mtshan du btags
NK071(du)005:36: zhi ba'i phrin las kyis nyon lnga ye shes lngar shar bas nyon mongs bdud bcom /
NK071(du)005:37: rgyas pa'i phrin las kyis phung lnga rigs lngar shar bas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK071(du)005:38: dbang gi phrin las kyis khams dang nyon rlung dag
NK071(du)005:39: pas skye 'chi med par 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom
NK071(du)005:40: / drag po'i phrin las kyis snang srid dag mnyam
NK071(du)005:41: du shar bas lha bu'i bdud bcom pas na bcom
NK071(du)005:42: / ste / rdo rje las rim las /
NK071(du)005:43: 'dud bzhi ma spangs rig pa'i gdeng gis bcom /
NK071(du)005:45: 'bras chos nyer lnga dang ldan pas na ldan ces te /
NK071(du)005:47: sku lnga la sogs che yon kun dang ldan //
NK071(du)005:49: yod med snang stong sogs kyi phyogs re'i mtha' dang bral bas 'das zhes /
NK071(du)005:51: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med /
NK071(du)005:54: rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK071(du)005:55: mtshan nyid skye 'jig 'pho 'gyur bral ba rdo rje'i chos bdun dang ldan pas na rdo rje /
NK071(du)005:58: de nyid gnyis med 'jig bral bas //
NK071(du)005:60: de yang bsam brjod dang bral ba'i thugsa kyi rigs
NK071(du)005:61: mchog dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la bdag dang dbyer
NK071(du)005:64: nges don dbyings ye gnyis med /
NK071(du)005:65: shes rab kyi lha yum sgyu ma dang /
NK071(du)005:67: de gnyis dbyer med pa'i dra ba de'i don ji
NK071(du)005:68: bzhin ston pa'i rgyud mchog snying po lasa bshad pa
NK071(du)005:70: gang la bshad na 'dir las smon bzang po'i skal
NK071(du)005:71: ba mchog dang ldan pa'i dbang po rno zhing theg
NK071(du)005:72: mchog 'dir 'jug pa la sgo lnga skyon dang bral
NK071(du)005:73: ba snod dang ldan pa'i slob bu la /
NK071(du)005:77: gzung ba dang 'dzin pas bsdus pa'i snod bcud kyi
NK071(du)005:78: yul lnga sogs ye nas lha yi rang bzhin yin
NK071(du)005:79: tshul bstan te de'i don mthong gamas mathara phyin par
NK071(du)005:80: byed na tshe 'dir sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob
NK071(du)005:81: pa'i phyir rgyu shes pa rkyen 'jug pa 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:82: mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid gsum sangs rgyas gsang ba
NK071(du)005:85: bar du dge ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:86: dang po gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi mdor bstan ni /
NK071(du)005:87: chos thams cad rtogs pa bzhi'i tshul gyis ye nas
NK071(du)005:88: sangs rgyas par shes nas sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i
NK071(du)005:89: mtshan nyid bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel du 'byor ba'i gzungsa
NK071(du)005:90: ni / 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi smin byed kyi rgyu dang rkyen la goms pas /
NK071(du)005:91: nus mthu khyad par can du gang gyur pa de ni /
NK071(du)005:92: 'bras bu bde bar gshegsa pa rnams kyi rigas mngon du bya ba'i ched /
NK071(du)005:93: gzhung don gyi yan lag rgyas bshad 'byung ba'i gzhi ru dgod de /
NK071(du)005:94: gnyis pa rgyas bar bshad pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK071(du)005:95: dang po gzhi'i mdor bstan ni /
NK071(du)005:96: mchog gi dngos grub kyi 'bras bu sgrub pa'i rnal
NK071(du)005:97: 'byor la rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba bshad
NK071(du)005:98: pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:99: dang po gzhal bya 'khor ba'i chos bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:100: de la so so'i skye bo'i dbang po lnga dang
NK071(du)005:101: yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg sogs yul du snang
NK071(du)005:102: ba kun sems kyi bag chags las yul dang dbang
NK071(du)005:103: po rnams snang ba sems nyid las logs na yod
NK071(du)005:106: grol 'khrul gyi gzhi kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid /
NK071(du)005:107: phyi nang gi yul shes kyi dngos po 'khor 'das
NK071(du)005:108: sna tshogas su ma 'gags par snang ba yi phyir
NK071(du)005:109: / zhen snang 'di gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab pa'i gzhi ru rung ngo //
NK071(du)005:111: nges par bzhag pa'i gzhal bya ni //
NK071(du)005:113: rang gi mtshan nyid mi 'dod do //
NK071(du)005:114: de ltar nang nas zhen pa yis //
NK071(du)005:115: phyir rol med la yod ltar snang //
NK071(du)005:116: zhen dang lta ba gnyis la brten //
NK071(du)005:118: gnyis pa gzhal bya rang gi ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:120: las dang po pa yi brtag gzhir de la lta ba 'tshol ba'i thabs su rung ba dang /
NK071(du)005:121: de nas gzod 'tshol ba'i tshe dang lta ba de la 'phel rim yod par bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:122: mthar phyin nas nges para bya ba lta ba rang
NK071(du)005:123: gi ngo bo dang gsum ste thoga ma'i lta ba
NK071(du)005:124: 'tshol ba'i tshe / gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK071(du)005:129: thos pa dang bsam byung gis lta ba rtogs pa'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:130: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab pa'o //
NK071(du)005:132: dang po spyir bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:133: rang la so sora rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi rgyu
NK071(du)005:134: dang ldan pas rgyud gzhung zab mos thos pa'i shes
NK071(du)005:135: rab kyi dbang po mchog dang ldan pas tshig yul
NK071(du)005:136: du byas pa la brten nas /
NK071(du)005:137: skyon yon phyed pasa don gyi rgyu shes par byas nas bsgom pa'am /
NK071(du)005:138: bsam byung gi shes rab kyis lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK071(du)005:139: tshe na'ang gsang ba snying po dang lam rim sogs
NK071(du)005:140: gzhung las grags pa'i gtan tshagas lnga /
NK071(du)005:142: rjes 'jug tshul tshig sogs rgyud las byung ba nyid dang /
NK071(du)005:143: tshig la'ang mi mthun pa dang mthun pa'i gtan tshigas kyis gtan la dbab pa gces so //
NK071(du)005:144: gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK071(du)005:146: gang gi sgo nas 'tshol ba'i rgyu rkyen ngos bzung ba ni /
NK071(du)005:147: gtan tshigs kyis 'tshol tshe rgyu rkyen dang ldan dgos te /
NK071(du)005:148: des na chos rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid yul du byas pa la dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK071(du)005:149: bla ma bshes gnyen gyis dngos lnga sogs kyi ngo sprod pa ni bdag po yi rkyen /
NK071(du)005:150: lta ba'i rim pa ngo sprad pa la de ma thaga pa'i rkyen /
NK071(du)005:151: blo rig dang basa gsang sngags la 'jug 'dod dad
NK071(du)005:152: pa dang dga' spro dang ldan pa rang bzhin gyi
NK071(du)005:153: dbang rnon dang / theg pa 'og ma la sbyangs
NK071(du)005:154: pa'i bag chags bzang po'i rgyud dang ldan pa'i sbyangs
NK071(du)005:155: pa'i dbang rnon ni rgyu'i rkyen no //
NK071(du)005:156: shes rab zab mos chos rnams rang bzhin med pa'i
NK071(du)005:157: ngang nas sgrib bral du gzigs pa'i spyan mchog rang
NK071(du)005:159: ye gdod ma nas dbyings ye gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi /
NK071(du)005:162: shes pa lnga ste yul dbang yid byed sogs sku
NK071(du)005:163: dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin dbyer med yin pa
NK071(du)005:165: gces gal che bar gong du smos pa'i thob bsam
NK071(du)005:166: la sogs gtan tshigs rnams ni lhan caga byed pa'i
NK071(du)005:167: rgyu'o // rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi de daga gi sgo nasa lta ba 'tshola bar byed pa la /
NK071(du)005:168: tshong pa rnams kun tu rgyu zhing rang gi 'dod don 'grub par smon par byed pa bzhin /
NK071(du)005:169: zab mo'i gnad dang mthar thug 'bras bu smon cing don du gnyer bar bya'o //
NK071(du)005:170: gnyis pa gang la 'tshol ba'i yul bstan pa /
NK071(du)005:171: rgyu rkyen de yisa gzhal bya gzung ba'i yul dang 'dzin pa'i shes pa'i spyod yul gyi mtha'a der /
NK071(du)005:172: yod pa dang med pa dang yod med kyi lung
NK071(du)005:173: du ma bstan pa lasa 'tshol na sgro skur lung
NK071(du)005:174: ma bstan gyi skyon gsum du 'adu bas /
NK071(du)005:175: lta ba mnyam pa nyid mi rnyed do //
NK071(du)005:176: kun brtags kyis bslad pa'i yod med lung ma bstan
NK071(du)005:177: de dag gang yang mi 'dod pas de dang phral
NK071(du)005:178: la / dag mnyam chen po'i lta ba 'atshala ba'o //
NK071(du)005:179: gsum pa gang 'tshol ba'i ngo bo /
NK071(du)005:180: 'on tang 'khor 'das gnyis mnyam rdzogsa pa gnyis med
NK071(du)005:181: kyi don rtogs pa na thams cad rig pa'i cho
NK071(du)005:182: 'phrul tsam du chos kun yin la rang bzhin bden
NK071(du)005:183: grub med pas gang du yanga min pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)005:184: // mtha' phyogsa re dang bral ba phyogs med bdag
NK071(du)005:185: nyid chen po yid kyi bsam pa dang ngag gi
NK071(du)005:187: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i don gyi bcud dbang
NK071(du)005:188: po lnga yis yul lnga gcoda pa'i dus su dbang
NK071(du)005:189: shes sems dang yul chos ye gdod ma nas 'khor
NK071(du)005:190: 'das dag mnyam chen por dbyer med yin pa'i phyir
NK071(du)005:191: / tshogs brgyad dam tshogs drug gi shasa pa yul
NK071(du)005:192: dang bcas pa ye shes lngar shar ba ni shes
NK071(du)005:193: rab kyi mchoga ma h+aa'i lta ba nges pa nyid
NK071(du)005:195: lta ba'i ngo bo ni rgyas par 'og nas 'chad do //
NK071(du)005:196: bzhi pa snod bstan pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:197: dang po rang bzhin dbang rnon cig char 'jug pa ni /
NK071(du)005:198: de ltar lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe ma h+aa'i theg pa la sems g.yo ba dang /
NK071(du)005:200: 'jug pa'i nganga tshul can de rang bzhin dbang rnon
NK071(du)005:201: dang ma h+aa'i dgongs don gnyis ngo bos bdag nyid
NK071(du)005:202: gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod pa'i phyir theg pa gzhan
NK071(du)005:203: ma sbyangs par gzhi sems can de nyid kyi thog
NK071(du)005:204: nasa 'dir ma h+aa yo ga'i theg par 'jug nges
NK071(du)005:205: pa'i lta ba'i don khong du chud bas 'jug tu
NK071(du)005:206: rung ba'o // gnyis pa sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon rim gyis 'jug pa la gsum /
NK071(du)005:207: dang po rim gyis pa'i cig car ba rgyu'i theg
NK071(du)005:208: pa la sbyangs nas ma h+aa la 'jug tshul ni
NK071(du)005:209: / la la ste sbyangs pa'i cig char ba thun
NK071(du)005:210: mong mtshan nyid theg chen kyi lam rnamas la gnas
NK071(du)005:211: nasa rkyen bzhi dang rgyus zhes rgyu gnyis 'tshogs pas
NK071(du)005:212: ma h+aa 'dir zhugs shing slob par ngasa pa'o //
NK071(du)005:215: snying por rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK071(du)005:216: bshes gnyen mgon la lung gnyis thob //
NK071(du)005:217: yon tan mthong dang skyon mthong dang //
NK071(du)005:218: des skyo rmongs bred dang bcas pa //
NK071(du)005:219: gnyis pa rgyu ru gsungs pa yin //
NK071(du)005:220: de bdag gsang sogs dmigs pa ste //
NK071(du)005:221: skad cig 'phel ba de ma thag /
NK071(du)005:223: gnyis pa rim gyis pa'i rim gyi pa phal ba'i
NK071(du)005:224: sems brgyad nas bzung yo ga man chad sbyangs nas
NK071(du)005:226: sbyangs pa'i gang zag kha cig 'jig rten phal pa'i sems brgyad nas brgyud cing sbyang bar bshad da /
NK071(du)005:228: rnam snang mngon byang sogs las gsungs pa ltar /
NK071(du)005:229: so skye'i rgyud la chos kyi 'du shes tsam skye ba ni sa bon lta bu dang po /
NK071(du)005:230: pha ma sogs la sbyin pa byas pa myu gu lta bu ste gnyis pa /
NK071(du)005:231: gzhan la sbyin pa sdong po lta bu ste gsum pa /
NK071(du)005:232: spyin pa des snod du rung ba 'tshol zhing sbyin pa lo ma lta bu ste bzhi pa /
NK071(du)005:233: bla ma sogs la phul ba me tog lta bu ste lnga pa /
NK071(du)005:234: gzhan dga' mgu ldan par sbyin pa 'bras bu lta bu ste drug pa /
NK071(du)005:235: mtho ris su skye ba'i phyir tshul khrims bsrung ba 'di gsos su gyur pa lta bu bdun pa /
NK071(du)005:236: 'jig rten pa'i lha dbang phyug dang tshangs pa sogs
NK071(du)005:237: mchod sbyin byas pa 'di ni stobs su gyur pa
NK071(du)005:238: ste sems brgyad yin par rgyal ba rnams kyis bshad
NK071(du)005:239: do // de la dang po gcig dad pa'i sems /
NK071(du)005:240: bar gyi lnga sbyin pa'i sems /
NK071(du)005:241: tha ma gnyis tshul khrims kyis rten yin par gsungs /
NK071(du)005:242: de nas brgyud de bskal ba sprul sku'i zhing khams
NK071(du)005:243: gcig gi rdul snyed du bgrang ba'i grangs dang mnyam
NK071(du)005:244: par sbyangs nas / thun mong rgyu'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)005:245: mchog gi theg pa yo ga man chad kyi lam
NK071(du)005:246: la sbyangsa pas de'i stobs kyis ma h+aa'i theg pa
NK071(du)005:248: gsum pa thun mong theg pa'i sa mthar phyin pa'i
NK071(du)005:249: 'bras bu kun tu 'od kyi sa nas ma h+aa'i
NK071(du)005:251: sbyangs pa kha cig thun mong rgyu'i theg pa'i lam
NK071(du)005:252: lnga sa bcu mthar phyin par byas nas 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:253: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pa'i tshe
NK071(du)005:255: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug
NK071(du)005:256: pa'i sku lnga gsung ma lnga thugsa lnga ste bco
NK071(du)005:257: lngasa lhun grub kyi 'khor la byin brlabs dbang bskur
NK071(du)005:258: ba dang / 'khor bcu gnyis pa pad+ma can gyi
NK071(du)005:259: sa la 'god par 'dod pa rnams dang 'tshams par
NK071(du)005:260: mos pa'i snang ba la dgongs pasa /
NK071(du)005:261: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug yum gyi bcu drug dang /
NK071(du)005:262: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug re re la'ang ye
NK071(du)005:263: shes lnga lnga'i rtsal dang ldan pas snang ba brda'
NK071(du)005:265: bcu gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo'i sa mchog thob pa la 'gyur bar ngasa pa'o //
NK071(du)005:266: lnga pa gang gis 'tshol bar byed pa'i thabs gtan tshigs kyis rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:267: dang po kun tu 'od kyi sa nas ma h+aa'i
NK071(du)005:268: 'bras bu la 'jug pa'i tshe sngon byung dngos lnga'i
NK071(du)005:269: gtan tshigs ni / 'jug tshul bzhi yod pa'i tshig gi mtha' ma'i 'bras bu kun 'od nas /
NK071(du)005:270: bcu gnyis pad+ma can gyi sa la 'jug pa'i tshe
NK071(du)005:271: na ston pa sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang
NK071(du)005:272: gis 'khor theg 'og rgyal ba rgya mtsho la /
NK071(du)005:273: bstan pa gsung lnga lhun gyis grub pa yasa don dngos su ston pa ni /
NK071(du)005:274: sngon byung dngos lnga'i lam zhes bya /
NK071(du)005:275: gnyis pa rjes 'jug gtan tshigs la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:276: bskal pa grangs med gsum du sbyangs pa'i las can sngon byung dngos dang tshul mthun gtan tshigs dang /
NK071(du)005:277: tshig gi tshul du gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)005:279: dang po lta ba 'tshol ba'i mos pa tha dad
NK071(du)005:280: kyi dbang gis tshul mthun du rtogs lugs mi 'dra
NK071(du)005:282: dngos lnga de'i rjes su 'jug pa da lta'i gang
NK071(du)005:283: zag gis rgyu shes pa'i lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe
NK071(du)005:284: / tshul bdun gyis blo'i mos pa tha dada kyi dbang gis phye bas na /
NK071(du)005:285: bde bar gashagas pa sku lnga'i gsung lnga yis 'khor
NK071(du)005:286: lnga la brda sprod pa de nyid kyi phyogs re'i
NK071(du)005:287: tshul mthun gyisa so sosa rang rang gi blo dang
NK071(du)005:289: gnyis pa 'jug pa'i rten gyi gang zag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK071(du)005:290: gtan la dbab pa'i gang zag dngos ni bskal pa
NK071(du)005:291: chen po gsum na'am grangs med gsum nas theg pa
NK071(du)005:292: 'og ma la sbyangs pa de yasa /
NK071(du)005:293: mthar zab mo gasnga sngags kyi tshig thos pa la mi skrag /
NK071(du)005:294: mi basnganga bar don go nas bzod pa thob pa dasa rtogs so //
NK071(du)005:295: gsum pa tshul gyi gtan tshigs dngos de la bdun te /
NK071(du)005:296: chos sku'i gsung dang tshul mthun pa brjod med tshul gyis gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK071(du)005:297: chos sku dngos kyi 'khor dngos la de'i gsung gi
NK071(du)005:298: sgo nas brda' sprad pa'i tshul bzhin du 'dir yang
NK071(du)005:299: chos rnams rang bzhin brjod pa med pa'i tshul gyis
NK071(du)005:300: don gya gnas lugs des gtan la dabba nas rtogs
NK071(du)005:301: so // longs sku'i gsung tshul mthong thos brda' yi sgo nas gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK071(du)005:302: longs spyod rdzogas pa'i sku'i gsung gis 'khor la brda' sprad pa lta bura /
NK071(du)005:303: bla ma dgongs pa mnyam par bzhag pa dang phyag
NK071(du)005:304: gi brda' yi dang dbyibs kha dog sogs kyi sgo
NK071(du)005:306: sprul sku'i gsung tshul tshig gi sgo nas gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK071(du)005:307: sprul pa sku'i brjod pa tshig gisa 'khor la brda' sprod pa'i gsung lta bura ni /
NK071(du)005:308: bla mas brjod pa'i tshig gi sgo nas rmal bar bya bas rtogs pa'o //
NK071(du)005:309: mngon byang gsung tshul rig pa'i byin rlabs kyis gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK071(du)005:310: mngon para byang chub pa'i skus 'khor la rig pa
NK071(du)005:311: byin rlabs kyi gsung gis de bzhin brda' sprad pa
NK071(du)005:312: lta bu / 'dir rang rig pa'i byin rlabs kyis ye shes lngar shar nas gtan la dabba pa'o //
NK071(du)005:313: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung tshul gyis grags stong dbyer med kyis gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK071(du)005:314: rda rje'i sku ya 'khor la dbyer med kyi gsung gis brda sprod pa lta bur /
NK071(du)005:315: sgra grag stong gnyis su meda pa mtha' dang bral
NK071(du)005:316: ba'i don gyi rang bzhin dbyer med kyis gtan la
NK071(du)005:318: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung dang tshul mthun par snang
NK071(du)005:319: srid mthong thos mnyam pa nyid du gtan la dbab
NK071(du)005:320: pa ni / gang zag la la 'ga' zhig gis
NK071(du)005:321: ngo bo nyid skus 'khor la mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK071(du)005:322: gsung gis brda' sprad pa ltar /
NK071(du)005:323: 'di ltar snang zhing srid pa'i chos thams cad mthong ba dang /
NK071(du)005:324: thos pa nyid kyisa ma brtags par snang stong mnyam pa nyid du gtan la 'bebas shing rtogs so //
NK071(du)005:325: gsang ba sku'i gsung dang tshul mthun par thabs lam gyi spyod pas gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK071(du)005:326: ston pa gsang ba sku yi 'khor mthar lam pa la /
NK071(du)005:327: bstan par dka' ba ye shes lnga lnga'i rtsal dang ldan pas brda' sprad pa'i gsung lta bura /
NK071(du)005:328: 'dir phyag rgya yum la spyod pa yi thabs kyis
NK071(du)005:329: bde stong gnyis med gtan la pheb cing rtogs par
NK071(du)005:330: 'gyur ro // gnyis pa tshig gi gtan tshigs la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:331: tshig gis gtan la dbab par bya ba dang 'bebs par byed pa dang /
NK071(du)005:332: go bar byed pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)005:334: dang po tshig rang ngos bzung ba na /
NK071(du)005:335: gong bstan tshul mthun gyi rtogs ma nus pa gang
NK071(du)005:336: zag la la kha cig la sngon byung sku bzhis
NK071(du)005:337: gsung bzhis bstan pa 'khor bzhi la brda' sprad pa
NK071(du)005:338: bzhin du 'dir tshig gis gtan la phab dgos te
NK071(du)005:339: / chos sku'i 'khor blo gros can la chos nyid
NK071(du)005:340: ji bzhin pa don dam ngesa pa'i gtan tshagas su
NK071(du)005:342: ston pa gsang ba'i skus 'khor chags zhen can gyi
NK071(du)005:343: gdul bya la 'dod pa ranga rkyen gyi blo dang
NK071(du)005:344: 'tshams pa'i gtan tshigas kyis ngo sprod pa dang /
NK071(du)005:345: ston pa longs skus 'khor dbang rnon la /
NK071(du)005:346: ldem por dgongs pas sbyor ba'i gtan tshigas kyi sgo nas ngo sprod pa dang /
NK071(du)005:347: ston pa sprul skus 'khor log sred can gyi gdul bya la /
NK071(du)005:348: theg pa 'og ma la bkri zhing gong ma la
NK071(du)005:349: drang zhing brgyud pa'i gtan tshagas kyis ngo sprod pa
NK071(du)005:350: bzhi po rnams / de gtan tshigs su 'gyur tshul
NK071(du)005:351: tshig gi sgo nas gdul bya so so'i blo la
NK071(du)005:352: nges par gtan la phab par byed cinga gtan tshigs
NK071(du)005:353: kyis brtag pa'i yul gzhal bya yongs su gzhiga cing
NK071(du)005:354: gtan la dbab par byed pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:355: dngos lnga'i dgongs don tshig tu sprad pa de dag
NK071(du)005:356: grub mtha' 'grub par byed pa'i byed las kyis gtan
NK071(du)005:358: gnyis pa gtan tshigs su ma gyur pa'i chos gzhan med par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:359: gong du bshad pa de basa na thams cad gtan
NK071(du)005:360: tshigas su bsgrub pa'i dbang btsan para byas na gtan
NK071(du)005:361: tshigas su ma gyur pa'i chos gang yang med do
NK071(du)005:362: // gnyis pa go bar byed pa'i tshul la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:363: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:364: de las re zhig tshig gi gtan tshigs kyi dbang du byas na /
NK071(du)005:365: dngos lnga po yi dgongs don tshig tu ngo sprad
NK071(du)005:366: nas gtan la phebs pa dpyad du med pa'i go
NK071(du)005:367: ba dang / gtan la mi phabas na dpyad du yod pa'i go ba gnyis so //
NK071(du)005:368: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:369: dang po tshig gis gtan la dbab mi dgos par dpyad du med pa'i go ba ni /
NK071(du)005:370: slar dbab tu med pa'i go ba ston pa la'ang
NK071(du)005:371: tshig gi gtan tshigs de nyid brjod pa yis grub
NK071(du)005:372: mtha'i don de nyid mthong zhing rnyed par byed pa'i
NK071(du)005:373: phyir dbab tu med pa rang gis go ba'i dgos
NK071(du)005:375: tshig don so sora rtog pa shes bya'i yul du 'gyur ba de bas na /
NK071(du)005:376: lta ba 'tshol ba'i tshe tshig gi gtan tshigs kyis
NK071(du)005:377: grub mtha' rtogs dgos pa'i phyir dpyad du med pa'i
NK071(du)005:378: gtan tshigs de ltar du ngesa so //
NK071(du)005:379: gnyis pa dpyad du yod pa'i go ba la gsum /
NK071(du)005:380: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:381: de la gcig shosa te dpyad du yod pa'i gtan tshigs la /
NK071(du)005:382: thun mong dang mchoga gi gtan tshigs gnyis so //
NK071(du)005:383: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:384: dang po dbu ma rigs sgrub la sogs pa thun mong gi gtan tshigs ni /
NK071(du)005:385: thun mong gi theg pa dbu ma'i gzhung las gragsa pa'i gtan tshigs la /
NK071(du)005:389: mu bzhi skye 'gog dang rnam pa bzhi dang sogas kyi sgras rten 'brel gyi dbu ma dang lnga'o //
NK071(du)005:390: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa gsang sngags kyi gtan tshigs la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:392: theg 'og dang thun mong min pa gsang sngags kyi gtan tshigs la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:393: gtan tshigs kyis tshig dang bsgrub bya'i don mthun para gtan la 'bebs pa yi tshe na dang /
NK071(du)005:394: gtan tshigas kyis gtan la dbab tshe bsgrub bya'i don
NK071(du)005:395: dang tshig mi mthun pasa grub mtha' gtan la 'abbas
NK071(du)005:396: par byed pa'o // gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:397: dang po tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK071(du)005:398: de la dang po tha snyad kyi chos kun gtan la 'abbas pa ni /
NK071(du)005:399: chos nyid de bzhin nyid gtan la 'abbas pa dang /
NK071(du)005:402: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar daga pa gsum dang /
NK071(du)005:403: yang log gnyis sam rnam grangs dang rnam grangs ma yin pa gnyis thun mong gi mnyam gnyis sam /
NK071(du)005:404: yang na kun rdzob sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad dang /
NK071(du)005:405: don dam spros pa'i mtha' brgyad de sngar sgyu 'phrul mkhan po dag gis bzhed /
NK071(du)005:406: kun rdzob sku dang ye shes dang /
NK071(du)005:407: don dam dkor bdun te lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis /
NK071(du)005:412: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med bdag nyid chen po
NK071(du)005:413: gnyis med kyi gtan tshigs dang la sogas kyi sgras
NK071(du)005:414: nyon mongs rang spyi'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK071(du)005:418: tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs la sogs pa'o //
NK071(du)005:419: gnyis pa de la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:420: dang po tshig don mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs dngos ni /
NK071(du)005:421: gnyis pa tshig don mi mthun pa la gtan tshigs /
NK071(du)005:422: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun rang rig pa la phyogs
NK071(du)005:423: gcig ci yang ma yina pas ma grub pa la
NK071(du)005:424: / phyogs med du ci yang yin pa dang thams
NK071(du)005:425: cad lhun gyis grub pa ltar snang yang rtag dngos
NK071(du)005:426: gzhi grub lta bu gang yang ma grub pa'i phyir
NK071(du)005:427: / / de la sogs pa ma spangs mi ldan
NK071(du)005:428: gyi sgo nas bsgrub bya'i don sgrub 'dod pa la
NK071(du)005:429: rgya mtsho'i nang gi gzugs brnyan ltar ci yang min
NK071(du)005:430: / / pa'i phyir / phyogs med du chos thams
NK071(du)005:431: cad kun gyi ngo bo yin pa'i phyir na ye
NK071(du)005:432: shes kyi snang bas yin phyir dang dbyings la 'khor
NK071(du)005:433: 'das zhes ma grub pas min phyir ma grub ces
NK071(du)005:434: / / pa'i phyir / / de phyir brjod pa'i
NK071(du)005:435: gtan tshigs la snang ba'i chos kun rig pa'i mdangs
NK071(du)005:436: las shar bas ma spangs la /
NK071(du)005:437: phyogs gcig tu zhen pa'am rang rgyud par med pa'i
NK071(du)005:438: cha nas mi ldan pa sogs kyis gtan la phab
NK071(du)005:439: pas so // gnyis pa tshig don mi mthun pa de gtan tshigs su gyur tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:440: de ltar yin ma yin grub ma grub sogs tshig
NK071(du)005:441: don mi 'dra ba la ltos nas gtan tshigs kyis
NK071(du)005:442: gtan la phab pa des rgyu byas nas ngo bo'i
NK071(du)005:443: grub mtha' grub pa'i phyir na /
NK071(du)005:444: tshig don mi mthun pa de daga grub mtha' grub
NK071(du)005:445: pa'i gtan tshigs su 'gyur bar ngasa pa de las
NK071(du)005:446: gsang sngags bla med kyi skabs 'dira gtan tshigs de
NK071(du)005:447: dag la brten nas rtogs dgos so //
NK071(du)005:448: gnyis pa gtan tshigs kyis gtan la 'bebs tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:449: thun mong gi gtan tshigs de yi gzhal bya de'i yul dang shes par snang ba dang /
NK071(du)005:450: mya ngan las 'das pa dang 'khor ba tha dad
NK071(du)005:451: du snang ba yi zhen pa gzhig par bya ba
NK071(du)005:452: la / thabs shes kyi sgo nas gtan la dbab dgos te /
NK071(du)005:453: de'ang rang rig pa la thabs 'gag med kyi rtsal
NK071(du)005:454: shar rgyu med na yul shes sam 'khor 'das kyi
NK071(du)005:456: thabs 'gag med kyi tshul 'char ba'i ngo bo nyid dang /
NK071(du)005:457: ji ltar 'char na de nyid rang rgyud can du
NK071(du)005:458: ma grub pas 'khor 'das kyi zhen pa de dag
NK071(du)005:459: ldog pa dang / de yang snang ba thams cad rang snang gi thabs chena po yin pa dang /
NK071(du)005:460: de ltar snang bzhin rang rgyud du ma grub pa
NK071(du)005:461: ni shes rab rang bzhin med pa nyid kyi lta
NK071(du)005:462: ba zung 'jug mnyam pa chen po gtan la phebs
NK071(du)005:463: pa'o // gnyis pa 'tshol ba'i tshe lta ba la 'phel rim yod par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:464: mdor bstan gyi bar ma lta ba'i 'phel rim bstan pa la /
NK071(du)005:465: bden pa dbyer med kyi sems nyid rtogs par byed pa rnam par nyams su len pa la /
NK071(du)005:470: mathara phyin pa'i sems lnga 'phel ba dang /
NK071(du)005:471: rgyu gcig yig 'bru byin rlabs mngon sum bzhi dang /
NK071(du)005:475: 'od gsal ba bzhi ste bzhi tshan gnyis kyis 'phel ba dang sogs kyi sgras bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang /
NK071(du)005:476: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lngas 'phel ba de
NK071(du)005:477: rnams kyi sgo nas snga mas phyi mar 'aphala ba'o
NK071(du)005:478: // de kun gcig spros tshogs lam bzhi'i grangs kyi
NK071(du)005:479: rim par snga phyir 'phel ba'ang yin pa 'dir shes
NK071(du)005:480: dgos te lam snga ma'i skabsa pas phyi ma'i skabs
NK071(du)005:481: nyid du rig pa la rang dbang thob cing 'phel
NK071(du)005:482: ba la the tshom meda do //
NK071(du)005:483: gsum pa mthar phyin nas nges par bya ba lta ba rang gi ngo bo la bzhi ste /
NK071(du)005:484: tshogs lam bzhi 'phel pa mthar phyir pa'i rtogs pa
NK071(du)005:485: bzhi'i tha ma mngon sum gyi rtogs pas gdeng du
NK071(du)005:486: gyur pa'i grub mtha' rang brten pa dang /
NK071(du)005:488: lam dang rgyud don lta ba'i skabs las shes shing ngo bo la rdzogs dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)005:490: dang po grub mtha' rang gi ngo bo bstan pa la dgu ste /
NK071(du)005:491: dang po dbyings rig gnyis gnyis med gzung 'dzin dang
NK071(du)005:492: bral ba'i rig pa dmigs med du snang tshul ni
NK071(du)005:493: / 'phel ba'i rim pa de dag gi mthar rnam
NK071(du)005:494: mthar bzhi'am mthas zhes rtogs pa mthar phyin nas lta
NK071(du)005:495: ba'i gdeng dang ldan pasa rtogs bya mnyam pa nyid
NK071(du)005:496: dbyings dang rtogs byed rig pa ye shes gnyis su
NK071(du)005:497: / med para / gsar du ma yin te ye
NK071(du)005:498: nas de bzhin nyid du dbyings ye dbyer med rdo
NK071(du)005:499: / med para / rjesa riga ste / de ltar
NK071(du)005:500: gzung 'dzina gnyis dang bral ba' rang riga pa de
NK071(du)005:501: nyid la dmigs bya dmigs byed med pa'i tshul du
NK071(du)005:502: rang snang dbyings ye dbyer med du snang ba'o //
NK071(du)005:503: gnyis pa gzhi don byang chub semas la dad nas dmigs byed med tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:504: gzhi don byang chub sems bden gsum dbyer med pa
NK071(du)005:505: de rnam pa 'di ltar du snang ba'i chos thams
NK071(du)005:506: cad la khyab cing snang ba ni /
NK071(du)005:507: snang stong phyogs rer shin tu blos brtag dka' ste
NK071(du)005:508: ci'i phyir zhe na rgya mtsho'i gting ltar zab pasa
NK071(du)005:509: na dngos po'i chos su ma dmigas dngos med kyi
NK071(du)005:510: chos su mi dmigas tha dad kyi chos su dmigs
NK071(du)005:511: su meda pa'o // gsum pa sems dang byang chub
NK071(du)005:512: dbyer med de dmigs bcas 'khor ba'i chos dang ldan
NK071(du)005:513: su meda pa'o // tshul ni / dmigs su med
NK071(du)005:514: pa'i semas nyid dbyer med de ni ji lta bu
NK071(du)005:515: su meda pa'o // tshul ni / yin zhe na
NK071(du)005:516: / don dam kun rdzob kyi byang chub de ni
NK071(du)005:517: semas dang dbyer med yin na //
NK071(du)005:518: des na sems dang byang chub la tha dad med cing dbyer med pa yin pasa na /
NK071(du)005:519: khams gsum gyi sems can ma lus thams cad dang /
NK071(du)005:520: 'das ma 'ongs da lta dus gsum gyi chos rnams
NK071(du)005:521: thams cad byang chub kyi sems su dbyer med yina
NK071(du)005:522: no // bzhi pa shes bya'i chos thams cad sems
NK071(du)005:523: dang byang chub la 'dus pas ye nas lhun grub
NK071(du)005:524: dag mnyam du yod tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:525: 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ma lus
NK071(du)005:526: mi lus lus pa med pa'i chosa so caga rnams
NK071(du)005:527: ni semas dang byang chub dbyer med nyid du 'uba
NK071(du)005:528: chub cing / de la thams cad shong bas yangas
NK071(du)005:529: shinga kun la khyab pas rgya che 'khor 'das gnyis
NK071(du)005:530: med lhun grub nyid du ni gnas so //
NK071(du)005:531: gtan tshigs de bas na phyi nang snod bcud thams
NK071(du)005:532: cad ye gdod ma nas sku dang ye shes su
NK071(du)005:534: de ltar lta ba dag par rtogsa pa nyid kyang
NK071(du)005:535: dbyings mnyam pa nyid yina par rtogs pa 'di ni
NK071(du)005:537: rdo rje mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings yin no //
NK071(du)005:538: lnga pa byang chub sems ni 'gro 'ong med par
NK071(du)005:539: rang gi rig par 'dus pas sangs rgyas dang sems
NK071(du)005:540: can kun sems la mnyam pa'i 'khor 'das mnyam tshul
NK071(du)005:541: ni / de ltar byang chub sems zhes su brjod
NK071(du)005:542: pa 'di ni dang po gang nas ma 'ongsa pa
NK071(du)005:543: mthar gara yang mi 'gro yul yul can gyi rtog
NK071(du)005:544: pa med par da ltar gyi rang gi riga pa
NK071(du)005:545: rang snang gsal la go ma 'gags pa kho na
NK071(du)005:546: tsam de la dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang khams
NK071(du)005:547: gsum gyi sems can rnams ni rang gi sems la
NK071(du)005:548: gansa pas 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid do //
NK071(du)005:549: drug pa mnyam pa'i don ni don dam rang bzhin
NK071(du)005:550: med pa dang kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bur shes
NK071(du)005:551: pa rang rig nyid du 'dus pas byed pa po
NK071(du)005:552: med par rang gsal yin tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:553: gong gi mnyam pa'i don nyid ji lta bu rtogs she na /
NK071(du)005:554: mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin phyogs gcig tu gang
NK071(du)005:555: yang grub pa med pas mana zhes mnyam pa dang
NK071(du)005:556: de la rtog pa yi 'dzin pa gnyis ka gang
NK071(du)005:557: yang mada la / chos thams cad ngo bo nyid
NK071(du)005:558: kyi rgyur gnas shing lhun gyis grub pa dang kun
NK071(du)005:559: rdzob rang rgyud can du ma grub pas sgyu ma
NK071(du)005:560: dang snang la rang bzhin med pa mig yor gyi
NK071(du)005:562: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med rang riga pa nyid du 'dus pa de bas na /
NK071(du)005:563: snang srid kyi chos rnams ma lus pa thams cad
NK071(du)005:564: kun rang bzhin ye gdod ma nyid nas dbyer med
NK071(du)005:565: du rnam par dag pa yina pa'i phyir byed pa
NK071(du)005:566: po sus kyang ma byas par sgrib byed med par
NK071(du)005:568: bdun pa de sangs rgyas kyi spyod yul yin pas skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:569: de lta bu su'i spyod yul yin zhe na /
NK071(du)005:570: blo phyogs zhen gyi mtha' la ma chags te dper
NK071(du)005:571: na pad+ma 'dam gyis ma gos pa dang 'dra ba
NK071(du)005:572: ya / rang byung gi ye shes rtogs pa'i spyan ldan gyi spyod yul yin la /
NK071(du)005:573: de nyid theg dman gdul bya kun dang thun mong du gyur pa de ma yina te /
NK071(du)005:574: de ni de bzhin gshegas pa'i spyod yul kho na yin no //
NK071(du)005:575: de'i sgras sus kyang mi rtogs sam zhe na /
NK071(du)005:576: de ni skyes bu blo rtsal dang ldan pa rab kyis rtogsa pa'o //
NK071(du)005:577: brgyad pa blta bya lta byed med par mthong tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:578: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad lhag ma ma lus
NK071(du)005:579: pa sems nyid du gcig pa'i nganga la blta ba'i
NK071(du)005:580: yul dang lta bar byed pa'i mkhan po gnyis su
NK071(du)005:581: byar med para sgrib bral ye shes gsal ba'i sgron
NK071(du)005:582: ma rgyun chad med par sgreng bas ni phyogs bcu'i
NK071(du)005:583: zhing khams thams cad rang snang tsam du mathanga ba'o
NK071(du)005:584: // dgu pa don tshig las byung yang lta ba
NK071(du)005:585: rtogs par byed pa la tshig gi sgra rkyang pa
NK071(du)005:586: la mi brten par blo yi gting du go dgos
NK071(du)005:587: // tshul ni / spyir mtshon bya'i chos thams cad
NK071(du)005:588: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab cing grub mtha' ma
NK071(du)005:590: mtshon byed lung rigs kyi tshig gisa mtshon pa las don gud dam logs shig na meda de /
NK071(du)005:591: tshig gi sgra nyid don gyi dngos po'am ngo bo rang mina no //
NK071(du)005:592: 'o na sgra don la 'brel ba med dam zhe na /
NK071(du)005:593: don nyid sgra las gud dam logs na meda kyang /
NK071(du)005:594: sgra nyid dang tshig phyogs gcig tu brjod pa ni
NK071(du)005:595: yang dag pa don gyi gnas lugs snying po ni
NK071(du)005:596: mina te / tshig gi dgos ched ni tshig gis don mtshon pa'am rtogs par byed pa'i thabs so //
NK071(du)005:597: de bas na mthar don rtogs pa'i tshe btags pa'i ming dang /
NK071(du)005:599: rjod pa'i sgra tsam la ma brten para don ji
NK071(du)005:600: lta ba bzhin blo yi gting du go bar byos
NK071(du)005:601: shig ces so // gnyis la rtogs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK071(du)005:602: dngos po thams cad chos nyid du grub pa la
NK071(du)005:603: gnyis las mchoga gi dngos grub kyi 'bras bu'am bcud
NK071(du)005:605: dang po lta ba'i don mngon sum du rtogs nas
NK071(du)005:606: 'khor ba mtha' med du mi gtong zhing byang chub
NK071(du)005:607: thob pa ni dper na chu srin gyi gre bar
NK071(du)005:608: rin po che chud na phyir mi gtong ba ltar
NK071(du)005:609: phyag rgya ji lta ba bzhin du lta ba rtogs
NK071(du)005:610: pa de la yon tan de ltar yod pa'i phyir
NK071(du)005:611: / gzhan don du 'khor bar skye ba du mar
NK071(du)005:612: bgrangs kyang rang ngo la ngan song 'khor ba'i gnas
NK071(du)005:614: gsum pa lam dang rgyud don lta ba'i skabs las
NK071(du)005:615: shes shing ngo bo la rdzogs dgos pa la drug
NK071(du)005:618: rnam grangs rnam par phye ba de dag gi skye ba'i rgyu dang /
NK071(du)005:619: zag bcas zag med kyi sa'i dbye bas mthong lam la gnyis su bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:620: zag ldog yod med kyi mu bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:621: zag bcas med pa'i lam la rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum yod lugs bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:623: dang po shes dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK071(du)005:624: tshonga dpon gyis don gnyer ba'i tshe lha ma grangs
NK071(du)005:625: mang mtha'i sar 'gro nas thams cad la bsam zhing
NK071(du)005:626: mkhas dgos pa bzhin du 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i ragas
NK071(du)005:627: lta ba'i skabs 'dir rig 'dzin bzhi man chad kyi
NK071(du)005:628: don la mkhas dgos pas de'ang rgyu shes pa'i mtshan
NK071(du)005:629: nyid shesa rab dang po lta ba'i mdor bstan la
NK071(du)005:630: smos pa'i skabs 'tshol lugs 'phel rim nges pa gsum
NK071(du)005:631: dang / bar du rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la
NK071(du)005:632: rgyu de ting dang mtshams sbyor kun ting dang 'brasa
NK071(du)005:633: bu phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis dang bar chad med
NK071(du)005:634: pa sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi shes rab
NK071(du)005:635: zab mos lta ba rnams rim par shes pa dang
NK071(du)005:636: dang / / zag bcas mtha' ru phyin pa'i 'bras bu mtshan nyi gsum ste gang zhe na /
NK071(du)005:637: tshe dbang gi lam kun gyi sngon du 'gro ba lta ba rtogs pa mthong lam pa dang /
NK071(du)005:638: phyag chen gyi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin mi g.yo ba bsgom lam pa dang /
NK071(du)005:639: goms pa mthar phyin pa lhun grub rig 'dzin mthar lam pa dang /
NK071(du)005:640: de rnams kyi shes rab lta ba'i mtho dman gyi
NK071(du)005:641: rim pa yod pa rnam lta ba'i skabs 'dir shes
NK071(du)005:643: gnyis pa ma shes pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK071(du)005:644: sems nyid rig pa bdag nyid chen po ma mthong zhing shes pa'i rgyud la ma sbyor basa /
NK071(du)005:645: sems nyid las gzhan du lta ba 'tshol zhing blo rmongs pa'i sems can kun gyis /
NK071(du)005:646: gsang sngags kyi lta ba bstan kyang rna bas ma
NK071(du)005:647: thos pa lta bu dang dpes mtshon kyang ma mthong
NK071(du)005:648: ba de basa na bdag dang gazhana gnyis tha dad
NK071(du)005:649: du phye nas lta ba 'tshol bas gang zag rnams
NK071(du)005:650: 'tshang mi rgya'o // de bas na lta ba yul sems mnyam pa nyid du rtogs par bya'o //
NK071(du)005:651: gnyis pa rgyud kyi lta grangs la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:652: rgyud don mdor bstan gyi sgo nas tshig tsam ma yin par mthong dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK071(du)005:653: dang po rgyud don mdor bstan pa la zlos pa gong 'og 'bru non par bya ba la /
NK071(du)005:654: mi gayo ba ting nge 'dzin bkod pa dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)005:655: ba bsrung ba dam tshig rala pa phrin las madzada
NK071(du)005:656: pa spyod pa gnas su stob /
NK071(du)005:657: mchod pa rim pa dbang don gnyer sgrub pa /
NK071(du)005:658: 'chinga phyag rgya zlos sngags te rgyud kyi dngos po bcu ste /
NK071(du)005:659: de yang ting 'dzin rnam gsum dang /
NK071(du)005:661: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig dang /
NK071(du)005:663: dge sbyong bag yod kyi spyod pa sogs gsum mam
NK071(du)005:664: sbyor sgrol gyi spyod pa dang phyi nang gsang ba
NK071(du)005:666: phan nus zab mo'i dbang dang /
NK071(du)005:667: mchog thun gyi dngos grub sgrub pa dang /
NK071(du)005:668: phyag rgya bzhi dang sngags gsum gyi lta ba rnams
NK071(du)005:669: chos nyid dag mnyam chen po'i gnad kyis ma zin
NK071(du)005:670: na cho ga gzugs brnyan tsam du zad de mchog
NK071(du)005:671: gi lam rnyed dka' bas na de ltar mngon sum
NK071(du)005:672: du shes shing / the tshom med par thag chod
NK071(du)005:673: par bya yi tshig tsam brjod shes pa la brten
NK071(du)005:674: pa mina pa de bas na lam gyi thog mar
NK071(du)005:675: lta ba'i skabs 'dir rgyud don gyi bye brag rnams
NK071(du)005:676: phyed nas don mngon sum du mthonga dgos pa'o //
NK071(du)005:677: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la dgu /
NK071(du)005:678: dang po mi g.yo ba ting 'dzin gyi lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:679: mnyam nyid spros bral thig le blos dpyad spros bral
NK071(du)005:680: las 'phags pas chen po'i lta ba rtogs pa'i rang
NK071(du)005:681: bzhin la rim gyis pas de ting kun snang rgyu'i
NK071(du)005:682: bsgom pa dang rnam pa gsum dus gcig tu rdzogsa
NK071(du)005:683: te / de'ang thig le chen po de nyid rgyu
NK071(du)005:684: rkyen gyis ma bcos shing mtha' gang du'ang mi g.yo
NK071(du)005:685: ba'i phyir na rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral ba
NK071(du)005:686: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi dbyingsa zhes so //
NK071(du)005:687: thig le de nyid kyi ngo bo la chos kun
NK071(du)005:688: gsal zhing sgrib bral gyi ye shes yin pa'i phyir
NK071(du)005:689: / de ni snod bcud kun tu rang snang gi ye shes kyi ngang zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)005:690: thig le chen po de nyid 'bras bu'i chos rnams kun gyi gzhi rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:691: de ni dbyer med kyi ye shes chen po'i dkyil
NK071(du)005:692: 'khor du gsal bas rgyu ya ting 'dzin dang gsum
NK071(du)005:693: po byed las kyi chas rim par ldan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:694: gnyis pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor gyi lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:695: rang rig pa byang chub ni de nyid dkyil 'khor yin te /
NK071(du)005:696: byang chub sems gsum 'du 'bral med pas snang stong
NK071(du)005:697: gi chos thams cad kun la dbyer med du 'khyil
NK071(du)005:698: bar gnas pa nyid dkyil 'khor te /
NK071(du)005:699: de ltar gzung 'dzin dang brala ba'i dbyings ye shes
NK071(du)005:700: de ni de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bzhugs gnas
NK071(du)005:701: so // kun gyi ngo bo'i gnas ni rten gzhal
NK071(du)005:702: yas khanga dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor zhi ba dang
NK071(du)005:703: so // / 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs kyi
NK071(du)005:704: pho nya nang du 'adu ba dang phyir 'phro ba
NK071(du)005:705: mang po dang ldan pa de'ang logs na snang ba
NK071(du)005:706: so // / ma yin te / de dag rang rig sems kyi cho 'phrul chen po yin no //
NK071(du)005:707: gsum pa bsrung ba dam tshig gi lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:708: rtsa ba'i dam tshig dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK071(du)005:709: ces bya ba rnams ni gud na logs shig tu
NK071(du)005:711: rang gi lta ba rnal ma'i don la mi 'da' ba dam tshig yina te /
NK071(du)005:712: khyad par sdom pa rnam ni rnam pa grangs la mi spang mi 'dor ba bcu dang /
NK071(du)005:713: rtsa ba lnga po sku gsung thugs gsum du dril
NK071(du)005:714: bas bcu gsum po dbye na sum brgya drug cu
NK071(du)005:715: dang / thun mong spyi yi dam tshig yo ga
NK071(du)005:716: man chad kyi srung thabs mtha' yas pa rnams thig
NK071(du)005:717: le chen po'i mnyam nyid lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang
NK071(du)005:719: bzhi pa rol pa phrin las kyi lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:720: phrin las bya ba yid yul dang byed pa'i mkhan
NK071(du)005:721: po gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis su las rnams
NK071(du)005:722: kun la thogas pa med par spyad /
NK071(du)005:723: zhi rgyas dbang drag bazha yi phrin las dang gcig
NK071(du)005:724: tu lhun gyi grub pa po yang thaga le chen
NK071(du)005:725: pa'i lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang du gasla te /
NK071(du)005:726: de yang dngos pora mtshan zhen bcoma pas drag po /
NK071(du)005:727: thams cad rang rig bdag nyid chen po'i dbang du bsdus pa ni dbang /
NK071(du)005:728: dkor bdun lhun gyis grub pas na rgyas pa /
NK071(du)005:729: gzung 'dzin gyi zug rngu gnyis dang bral bas zhi
NK071(du)005:730: ba ste phrin las kyi lta ba rtogs shing mthong
NK071(du)005:731: ba'o // lnga pa mdzad pa spyod pa'i lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:732: bdag dang gzhan gyi don spyod pa rnam pa gnyis
NK071(du)005:733: po yang thig le chen pa'i lta ba rtogs pa'i
NK071(du)005:735: spyod pa phyogs gcig par ci la'ang blos mi gnas
NK071(du)005:736: par bdag gzhan gyi don kun la thogs pa med
NK071(du)005:737: pa spyod / spyod dus spyod para byed pa'i mkhan
NK071(du)005:738: po dang spyad pa yi dngos po gnyis su zhen
NK071(du)005:739: pa spyod / pa meda do // drug pa gnas su stob pa mchod pa'i lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:740: mchod pa'i yo byad steng 'og gi rgyan dang phyi
NK071(du)005:741: nang gsang ba'i langas spyod 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pa
NK071(du)005:742: kun / dbul bya yi yul dang 'bul byed kyi
NK071(du)005:743: mkhan po gnyis dang de rnams la mchod pa'i las
NK071(du)005:744: kun / sogs de yang / gzhan du ma grub
NK071(du)005:745: pa rig pa byang chub kyi sems chen po de
NK071(du)005:746: yi rtsal cha 'phrul 'gag pa med pa mchod pa'i
NK071(du)005:747: dngos po rnams dbyer med bdag nyid chen po'i lta
NK071(du)005:749: bdun pa rim pa dbang gi lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:750: rig pa bdag nyid chen pa'i rang byung gi ye
NK071(du)005:751: shes lta ba rtogs pa'i ngang la phan nus zab
NK071(du)005:752: gsum gyi dbang lnga logs nas ma btsal bar dus
NK071(du)005:753: gcig lhun grub tu rdzogs pas 'thob bya yi don
NK071(du)005:754: dang thob byed kyi thabs thob par byas pa'ang gzhan
NK071(du)005:755: na med pa rang rig par dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir
NK071(du)005:756: gzhan nas dbang thob pa med do //
NK071(du)005:757: brgyad pa don du gnyer ba sgrub pa'i lta ba ni /
NK071(du)005:758: rig pa bdag nyid chen po la sku dang ye
NK071(du)005:759: shes lhun gyis grub cing gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa
NK071(du)005:760: ka nas dag pas dngos grub gsar du sgrub tu
NK071(du)005:761: med cing sgrib pa'ang gsar du spang du med la
NK071(du)005:762: sems chos nyid kyi nganga du sa lam bgrod du
NK071(du)005:764: 'bras bu logs nas 'ong ba med de gzhi'i de
NK071(du)005:765: bzhin nyid kyi ngang du lam dang 'bras bu thams
NK071(du)005:766: cad gnyis su med pa la /
NK071(du)005:767: bsgrub par bya ba dang sgrub par byed pa gnyis ga la yoda de med do //
NK071(du)005:768: dper na sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul rta glang gso bskyed
NK071(du)005:769: las ma byung ba ltar mchog thun dngos grub du
NK071(du)005:770: mar snang yang rgyu rkyen dang bral cing de bas
NK071(du)005:771: na don du gnyer ba bsgrub pa'nga lta ba rtogs
NK071(du)005:772: pa'i ngang du chud cing shes para bya'o //
NK071(du)005:773: dgu pa 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag rgya la gsum /
NK071(du)005:775: sngags brag ca'i sgra bzhin dang /
NK071(du)005:776: phyag rgya chu zla yi gzugs bzhina du /
NK071(du)005:777: sgra grags pa'i dus grags stong dang /
NK071(du)005:778: gzugs snang stong chu zla ltar rang rgyud par ma
NK071(du)005:779: grub pas lha sngags bskyed bzlas rnams yod med kyi
NK071(du)005:780: mtha' dang brala bar dbyer med du rtogsa pa'o //
NK071(du)005:781: gnyis pa sngags phyag rgya'i ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:782: dang po phyag rgya'i ngo bo ni /
NK071(du)005:783: phyag rgya chen po'i ngo bo'am mtshan nyid ni gang zhe na /
NK071(du)005:784: phyogs bcu na bzhugs shing dus bzhir gshegs pa yi
NK071(du)005:785: rgyal ba rnams kyi sku gsung thugs gsum dang dgongs
NK071(du)005:786: pa ye shes lnga po rnams bdag gi lus ngag
NK071(du)005:787: yid gsum dang dbyer med du rtogs pa las mi
NK071(du)005:788: 'da' bas phyag rgya cha zhes chen po dang /
NK071(du)005:789: spros pa'i lha'i sku phyag rgya bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)005:790: po de yang thig le chen po lta ba rtogs
NK071(du)005:791: pa de nyid las gzhan du grub pa'am bsgrub pa
NK071(du)005:793: gnyis pa sngags kyi ngo bo ni /
NK071(du)005:794: sngags zhes bya ba rab tu brjod pa yang /
NK071(du)005:795: don dama rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK071(du)005:796: kun rdzoba 'gag pa med pa gnyis dbyer meda par
NK071(du)005:797: rtogs pa'i lta ba mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor chana po
NK071(du)005:798: de ru / rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge +aahmh'u gsum dang /
NK071(du)005:799: de la sogs te rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)005:800: mtshon byed kyi yi ge zhe gnyis rnams 'dus par
NK071(du)005:801: rtogs pa'o // gsum pa sngags phyag rgya'i nges tshig ni /
NK071(du)005:802: rgyun chad med par rtag tu mnyam par bzhag pa
NK071(du)005:803: las mi 'da' bas na phyag rgya yi nges tshig
NK071(du)005:804: yina cing / nyon mongs chags sdang gti mug gsum
NK071(du)005:805: dang dus gsum gyi rtogs pa thams cad gting nas
NK071(du)005:806: 'byin pa'i phyir sngagsa kyi nges tshig yin no //
NK071(du)005:807: gsum pa rnam grangs rnam par phye ba de dag gi skye ba'i rgyu ni /
NK071(du)005:808: lta ba'i rnam grangs rnam par phye ba de dag kun gyi rgyu gangs las byung zhe na /
NK071(du)005:809: grol lam gyi dbang du thos bsam sgom pa la
NK071(du)005:810: brtan pa thob pa'i rgyu las lta ba byung ba
NK071(du)005:811: dang / thabs lam las byung ba la gnyis las dang po steng sgo ltar g.yas rtsa rkyang ma /
NK071(du)005:812: g.yon ro ma'i rtsa'i nang du rlung sems rgyu ba
NK071(du)005:813: dbu mar zhugs gnas thim gsum las lta ba skye
NK071(du)005:814: ba dang / gnyis pa 'og sgo ltar chagas pa
NK071(du)005:815: lam g.yas yab dang g.yon yum dang mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)005:816: ba dpe'i ye shes dga' bzhi'i lam las mchog tu
NK071(du)005:817: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba'i lta ba skyes pa'i rgyur
NK071(du)005:818: ba dang / byas so // grol lam blo chung
NK071(du)005:819: bas bsgom pa nas brgyud pa'i tshogs lam rnal 'byor
NK071(du)005:820: bzhi mthar phyin pa las lta ba skyes pa'i rgyur
NK071(du)005:822: bzhi pa zag bcas zag med kyi sas phye ba'i mthong lam la gnyis su bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:823: de ltar rgyu byas pa des zag bcas zag med
NK071(du)005:824: kyi sa yi mtho dman gyi cha yisa phye ba
NK071(du)005:825: ni lus snang sems gsum zung 'jug rig pa'i mngon
NK071(du)005:826: sum du nus pa thob pa zag med tshe dbang
NK071(du)005:827: dang de nyid rtogs kyang nus pa ma thob pa
NK071(du)005:828: zag bcas spros pa gnyis kyis phye ba'i khyad par
NK071(du)005:829: las / zag bcas mthong lam dang zag med mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yina no //
NK071(du)005:830: lnga pa zag ldog yod med kyi mu bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:831: zag pa ni tshogs sgrub man chad la yod pa ni /
NK071(du)005:833: rtogs pa'i rtsa ba phyi nang gi //
NK071(du)005:834: kun nas zag pa rnam pa lnga //
NK071(du)005:835: zhes nyon mongs dang nye ba'i nyon mongs gnyis bshad pa rtsa ba nyon mongs dang /
NK071(du)005:836: yan lag khams dang skye gnas 'chi 'pho ba dang bzhi'o //
NK071(du)005:838: spros pa man chad ngan 'gror ldog la /
NK071(du)005:839: tshogs sgrub ni ngan song du mi ldog pas de la gnyis yod de /
NK071(du)005:841: lta sgom gyi nus pa che chung gi mthu yisa phye bas na /
NK071(du)005:842: spros pa man chad dam tshig nyams na ngan 'gror ldog pa'ang yod de /
NK071(du)005:844: de phyir lam bzhir ldog zag yod //
NK071(du)005:846: tshogs sgrub ni dam tshig nyams mi srid pas ngan song du mi ldoga go //
NK071(du)005:847: zag pa ni sngon gyi skabs su bshad pa'i rgyu shes pa lta ba'i skabs kyi /
NK071(du)005:848: 'tshol yul 'phel rim nges pa gsum dang /
NK071(du)005:849: rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin la tshogs lam rnal
NK071(du)005:850: 'byor bzhi sbyor lam tshogs sgrub dang lnga ste brgyad
NK071(du)005:851: la yoda do // zag bcas mthar phyin pa 'bras
NK071(du)005:852: bu'i mtshan nyid rgyu shes pa tshe dbang dang rkyen
NK071(du)005:853: 'jug pa phyag chen dang mthar phyin pa lhun grub
NK071(du)005:854: dang gsum la ni lta sgom nus pa mthu can
NK071(du)005:855: du gyur nas mnyam rjes 'dres pas na zag ldog
NK071(du)005:856: gnyis ga la yoda de med do //
NK071(du)005:858: zag pa med la ldog pa yod pa'i mu 'dir mi bshad pa'ang gsungs /
NK071(du)005:859: drug pa zag bcas med lam la rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum yod lugs bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:860: zag bcas dang zag med kyi skabs gnyis la'ang /
NK071(du)005:861: zag bcas mthar phyin tshogs sgrub dang /
NK071(du)005:862: zag med mthar phyin lhun grub ste /
NK071(du)005:863: mthar phyin rnam pa gnyis yod pa'i phyira na /
NK071(du)005:864: zag bcas dang zag med gcig ste re re la'ang
NK071(du)005:865: rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum gsum dang ldan pa yin te
NK071(du)005:866: / de'ang zag bcas kyi gsum ni /
NK071(du)005:867: lta ba spyi'i tshul du rtogs pa rgyu /
NK071(du)005:868: de ting nas spros pa man chad rkyen /
NK071(du)005:874: de bas na spyi yi rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum ni /
NK071(du)005:876: rkyen 'jug pa de nyid nas tshogs sgrub man chad /
NK071(du)005:877: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa rig 'dzin dang sangs rgyas yin par shes par bya zhing /
NK071(du)005:878: bye brag rig 'dzin bzhi'i rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)005:879: bzhi pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:880: dang po ma rtogs pa'i skyon dngos ni /
NK071(du)005:881: gong bstan ltar lta ba gang gi don bshad pa
NK071(du)005:882: ltar ma rtogsa pa'i blo ngana pa ste shes rab
NK071(du)005:883: chung ba rnams gzhi don mnyam par ma rtogs pa
NK071(du)005:884: tshig bzang po la khungs phyung nasa lta ba ma
NK071(du)005:885: rtogsa te gdod bya longs yod snyam pa dman pa'i
NK071(du)005:886: le lo dang spyod pa rang kha mar shor ba
NK071(du)005:887: snyom las gnyis byas nas rang gzhan gyi don ma
NK071(du)005:888: grub par ngan song du 'gro ba'i skyon yod pa
NK071(du)005:889: de bas na sems nyid kyi don 'khor 'das mnyam
NK071(du)005:890: pa nyid ma rtogs na tshiga gi sgo nasa 'khor
NK071(du)005:891: 'das mnyam pa nyid yin pas na zhes brjod pa
NK071(du)005:893: gnyis pa de nas rtogs pa'i thabs la 'bad par gdams pa ni /
NK071(du)005:894: skyon 'dug pa de bas dana dang tshig ldan par byos shes zhes so //
NK071(du)005:895: 'on tang go ba la don med dam snyam na
NK071(du)005:896: the tshom med pasa go na mthar thug 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:897: 'grub pa'am yang na tshig la don med dam zhe
NK071(du)005:898: na ma yin te tshig la brten nas dad mos
NK071(du)005:899: byas na 'bras bu the tshom med par 'grub bo
NK071(du)005:900: zhes bya'o // spyi don gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:902: 'bras bu sgrub par byed pa'i rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la /
NK071(du)005:903: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK071(du)005:904: lta bsgom bogs 'don gyi spyod pa gnyis so //
NK071(du)005:905: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:910: bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor la rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la yang /
NK071(du)005:915: tshogs sgrub rnam pa lnga yod pa ste /
NK071(du)005:916: gnyis pa rgyas bshad la gsum /
NK071(du)005:917: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi sbyor lam tshogs sgrub dang lnga'i lam 'grod tshul rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:918: de lnga'i skabs na las rkyen gyi 'chi ltas byung na 'pho ba bsgom tshul dang /
NK071(du)005:919: lta sgom gnyis kyi skabs na rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum
NK071(du)005:920: dang ldan zhing re re la'ang dgos ched gnyis gnyis
NK071(du)005:921: yod cing rim cig char gyi sgo nas 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:922: la sbyor dgos par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:923: dang po la lnga yod pa las /
NK071(du)005:924: rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum dril ba gsum ste /
NK071(du)005:925: zag bcas lam gyi rgyu de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK071(du)005:926: rgyu 'bras mtshams sbyor ba'i rkyen kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK071(du)005:927: zag bcas kyi 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:929: dang po lam gyi rgyu yin pas dang por bsgom dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:930: dbyings ye gnyis sku gsung thugs yon phrin las lnga
NK071(du)005:931: ste 'phags pa'i dkor nor bdun po'i dngos po de
NK071(du)005:932: nyid ni rang rig pa sems nyid bcos slad dang
NK071(du)005:933: bral ba'i don dam pa ni shes bya kun gya
NK071(du)005:934: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu yin pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:935: dbu ma pa'i don dam las lhag pa ni gsang
NK071(du)005:936: sngags pa'i rgyu de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)005:938: de'ang lam gyi thog mar tshogs lam dang por bsgom mo //
NK071(du)005:939: gnyis pa de ting rang gi sems kyi bzhag thabs ni /
NK071(du)005:940: de'ang bsgom tshul ni bsam bya yi chos nyid ces
NK071(du)005:941: bya ba zhig blos dmigs nas bsam par mi bya
NK071(du)005:942: ste / 'o na mi bsam par yin no bar snyam pa yang blos mi bsam ma //
NK071(du)005:943: ci'i phyir na de ka rang blo yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)005:944: de bas bsam bya bsam byed kyi 'adu shes kyi
NK071(du)005:945: 'dzin pa kun dang brala bar bsgom pa ni ting
NK071(du)005:947: gsum pa skyon bcos thabs ni /
NK071(du)005:948: gong gi de bas na rang gi semas nyid gsal
NK071(du)005:949: stong zung 'jug rtogs par byas pa ni gal che
NK071(du)005:950: ba yin te / lam chen las bshad ltar le
NK071(du)005:951: lo la sogs g.yeng ba thams cad yongs su spangs
NK071(du)005:952: ba yin te / la / gang zag gi nga
NK071(du)005:953: dang chos kyi bdag med pa'i don la mnyam par
NK071(du)005:954: mi 'da' bar bsrung zhing gsal stong mnyam pa'i dam
NK071(du)005:956: bzhi pa ngo bo'i thog la pheb pa'i tshad bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:957: yid kyi shes pas gsal cha'i bye brag phyed pa
NK071(du)005:958: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du damgas pasa gtad bya'i
NK071(du)005:959: yul dang bral ba gsal stong zung 'jug tu ngo
NK071(du)005:960: 'phrod cing bsgom pa ni lta ci smos /
NK071(du)005:961: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi spyod yul gyi 'char sgo
NK071(du)005:962: rnams rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes su gyur
NK071(du)005:963: pasa na / tshogs drug gi 'char sgo snang ba
NK071(du)005:964: rnams dus gcig tu gasla stong zung 'jug tu shar
NK071(du)005:965: ba de yi phyir shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa
NK071(du)005:966: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes thob thabs kyi rgyu'i bsgom
NK071(du)005:967: pasa na / pa yin no // gnyis pa rkyen kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:968: dang po rgyu 'bras mtshams sbyor gyi rkyen yin pa'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:969: dang po de ltar rgyu de bzhin nyid la brtan pa thob pa de yisa /
NK071(du)005:971: 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis tha dad du
NK071(du)005:972: mi gtang ba'i phyir rgyu 'bras mtshams sbyor gyi rkyen
NK071(du)005:973: kun snang ting 'dzin bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)005:974: gnyis pa kun snang gi ngo bo la phyag rgya
NK071(du)005:975: sgyu ma 'dir bsgom pa'i skabs min par bstan pa
NK071(du)005:976: ni / kun ting de la yang gnyis yod pa yin te /
NK071(du)005:979: dngosa po sgyu ma gnyis las /
NK071(du)005:980: phyag rgya sgyu ma ni kun ting gi skabs 'dir
NK071(du)005:981: shes mod kyang dngos su sgom pa'i dus min pa'i
NK071(du)005:983: dngos po sgyu mar bsgom pa'i thabs yul bral gyi
NK071(du)005:984: snying rje 'di ni 'og ma'i snying rje las dpags
NK071(du)005:985: shing skyabs kyi yul du gyur pas de la zhen
NK071(du)005:987: phyag rgya sgyu ma las dgar bas gcig shos dngos
NK071(du)005:988: po sgyu ma bsgom pa ni rang rig pa'i ngo
NK071(du)005:989: bo la / 'bras bu sdug bsngal dang rgyu nyon
NK071(du)005:990: mongas pa rnams ngang gisa rang rgyud du grub pa
NK071(du)005:991: mada de dngos po phyi nang gi snang ba kun
NK071(du)005:992: tu rig pa rang gsal ba'i ye shes kyi ngang
NK071(du)005:993: la snying rje skye bya'i yul dang /
NK071(du)005:994: skye byed kyi mkhan po gnyis su med pa'i don
NK071(du)005:995: gya gnas lugs rtogs shing bsgom pas na mtshan nyid
NK071(du)005:996: theg pas mas bu la gdung ba dang 'dra ba'i
NK071(du)005:997: snying rje las mchoga ma h+aa yo ga'i gnyis med
NK071(du)005:998: kyi ngang du sems can yongas su grol ba'i las
NK071(du)005:999: de nyid kyi ni skyabs kyis phul du byung ba'i
NK071(du)005:1000: yul bral gnyis med kyi snying rje de lta bas
NK071(du)005:1001: mthong nas sgom pas de la zhen pa de ya
NK071(du)005:1002: ma bral bar bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)005:1003: de ltar lta bas mthonga zhing ting 'dzin goms pa su yod pa la gong ma'i don 'byung ste /
NK071(du)005:1004: de'ang rgyu rkyen gnyis kyi don dang ldan pa la
NK071(du)005:1005: gsum pa 'bras bu gcig spros kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)005:1007: gsum pa zag bcas kyi 'bras bu bstan pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1008: 'bras bu'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1011: rkyen kun snang la brtan pa thob nas 'bras bu grub tshul bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1012: kun snang de la brtan pa thoba pasa 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:1013: phyag rgya gcig spros kyi don rnams grub pa'i phyir
NK071(du)005:1014: / gnyis pa de nyid bsgom tshul la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1016: de nas 'bras bu phyag rgya gcig pa dang spros
NK071(du)005:1017: pa'i ting 'dzina gyi rim pa rnams go rim bzhin
NK071(du)005:1019: de yang samas nyid rig pa rang yi ge ru
NK071(du)005:1020: gsal ba dang phyag rgya ste phyag mtshan du gsal
NK071(du)005:1021: ba dang / sku yi ngo bora gsal ba'ang rig pa rang snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK071(du)005:1022: 'bras bu phyag rgya gciga pa dang sgros pa bsgom pa'ang 'og nas 'byung ba ni 'di ltar te /
NK071(du)005:1023: gnyis pa bsgom thabs rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:1024: dang po la phyag rgya gcig pa sgom thabs dang /
NK071(du)005:1025: de nas spros pa sgom thabs so //
NK071(du)005:1027: dang po zhi ba phyag rgya gcig pa sgom thabs ni /
NK071(du)005:1028: sngon de ting dang kun ting gi rjes su'am /
NK071(du)005:1029: sngon mdor bstan gyi rjes su phyag rgya gcig pa la bsgom par byas nasa /
NK071(du)005:1031: bye brag sgom tshul rnal 'byor rang gi riga pa
NK071(du)005:1032: la ngo bo dbyibsa rang rgyud dam phyogs gcig tu
NK071(du)005:1033: grub pa meda pa las 'dir yig 'bru dang kha
NK071(du)005:1034: doga phyogs gcig tu grub pa mada pa'i rang mdangs
NK071(du)005:1035: kyi kha dog ni rigs lnga gang rung gi kha
NK071(du)005:1037: 'dir thugs kyis gtsor byas pa'i dbang du h'u bsgom pa ste /
NK071(du)005:1038: de la kha daga rang rgyud pa meda bzhin du
NK071(du)005:1039: sngo zhes sngon po dbyibsa rang rgyud du grub pa
NK071(du)005:1040: mada pa'i thugsa kyi yig 'bru h'u rang rig tu
NK071(du)005:1041: shar ba la brtan pa thob nas phyag rgya ste
NK071(du)005:1042: thugs phyag mtshan dang sku phra mo gnyis rim bazhana
NK071(du)005:1044: mthar sku phra mo yongas su 'gyur ba las sku
NK071(du)005:1045: phyag rgya chen po zhal gciga pa ni don rang
NK071(du)005:1046: byung gi ye shes dang ldan pa'i rtags so //
NK071(du)005:1047: phyag gnyis thabs dang shes rab rtags so //
NK071(du)005:1048: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu dang bcas pa tshanga bar byas nas dam tshig pa bskyed la /
NK071(du)005:1049: ye shes pa rang bzhin gyi gnas nas snyan gsan phab /
NK071(du)005:1052: bstod pa bzlas pa dang bcas pa dkyil chog ltar bya /
NK071(du)005:1053: zhal gcig phyag gnyis de la gamas nas rnam thar
NK071(du)005:1054: gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags zhal gsum ye shes drug
NK071(du)005:1055: dang ldan pa'i rtags phyag drug bsgom pa la'ang phrin
NK071(du)005:1056: las kyi rim pa gong gi de bzhin no //
NK071(du)005:1057: gnyis pa khro bo sgom thabs ni /
NK071(du)005:1058: yang na khro bor mas pasa na khros pa khro bora bsgom pa /
NK071(du)005:1059: de yang zhi ba phyag rgya gcig pa de yi tshul bzhin du bya'o //
NK071(du)005:1060: gsum pa spyod lam lha yi dal du khyer thabs ni /
NK071(du)005:1061: de dag bsgom pa'i dus su spyod yul tshogs drug
NK071(du)005:1062: gi snang ba de nyid lha'i sku phyag rgyar gsal
NK071(du)005:1063: zhing sgo gsum de las mi 'da' bar bsdomsa nas
NK071(du)005:1064: bsgom mo // gnyis pa spros pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1065: dang po rim par bskyed cing spro lugs bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1066: phyag rgya gcig pa la brtan pa thob nas lha du mar spros pa'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa la /
NK071(du)005:1067: zhi khro ganga la'ang sngon rgya gcig skabs su zhi khro bsgom pa la gzhi byas pa'i /
NK071(du)005:1068: zhal phyag gi grangsa spros pa dang phyag rgya'i grangs spros pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1069: gnyis pa gang spro ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1070: dang po zhal phyag spros pa la dbu gsum phyag drug dang /
NK071(du)005:1071: de nas dbu lnga dang phyag bcu /
NK071(du)005:1072: de nas dbu dgu dang phyag bco brgyad dang /
NK071(du)005:1073: de nas dbu nyi shu rtsa gciga phyag zhe gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1074: de nas dbu ba rgya phyag brgyad brgya la sogs
NK071(du)005:1075: zhala phyag grangs med kyi bar du spro ba dang
NK071(du)005:1076: / gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rnam grangs spros pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1079: de nas rigs lnga dang de nas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyisa dang /
NK071(du)005:1080: de nas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ragas gcig yab yum la bkod pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1081: de nas rigs lnga yab yum la bkod nas spros sama /
NK071(du)005:1082: yang na blo chung na tshom bu'i grangsa gcig gsum
NK071(du)005:1083: lnga'i rim pa bzhin bslab cing spros nas byin gyis
NK071(du)005:1084: brlabs so // gnyis pa mthar rdzogs tshul bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1085: de dag la rim par gomas nasa brtan pa thob
NK071(du)005:1086: pas na phyis lha bsgom pa la dper na chu
NK071(du)005:1087: las nya ldang ba'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)005:1088: skad caga gis sngags brjod pasa na lha tshogs rnams
NK071(du)005:1089: kyi sku 'od du 'bar ba lha stong ga dkyil
NK071(du)005:1090: 'khor man chada du rang riga pa'i mngon sum gsal
NK071(du)005:1091: zhing shar ba ni mathara phyin pa'i tshad yin pa'o
NK071(du)005:1092: // gnyis pa de sgrub pa'i thabs la gsum ste /
NK071(du)005:1093: dang po sgrub pa'i thabs dngos bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1094: rnal 'byor pa rab kyis lha stong dang khri tsam
NK071(du)005:1095: gsal na bsgrub tu rung ba ni ci smos dgos
NK071(du)005:1096: te / tha mas tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i
NK071(du)005:1097: lha la'ang shin tu brtan nasa gsal na bsgrub tu
NK071(du)005:1098: rung ste gnas skor khanga sum rim dang ldan par
NK071(du)005:1099: te / byas nas / lta sgom gyi ngang nas bro gar gyi yo byad dang /
NK071(du)005:1103: gsang ba +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad lnga la
NK071(du)005:1104: sogas pa'i tshogs kyi spyod pa rnams dang ldan par
NK071(du)005:1105: byas te / de'ang bsnyen pa dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK071(du)005:1106: sgrub pa dang sgrub pa chen po bzhi'i sgo nas
NK071(du)005:1107: sgrub pa la spros pa mthar phyin pa'i dus kyi
NK071(du)005:1108: tshogas sgrub la sbyar nas bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1109: gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i dus nye ring gi rgyu mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1110: de'ang yang rab rab kyis zla ba drug 'bring gis zla ba bcu gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1111: mtha' ltag gis zla ba bcu bzhi /
NK071(du)005:1112: mtha' mas zla ba bcu drug gi mtha' mar 'bras bu grub ste /
NK071(du)005:1113: de'ang dus la nye ring yod pa'i khyad par /
NK071(du)005:1117: ting nge 'dzina 4nus pa che chung ngam gsal mi
NK071(du)005:1118: gsal gyi khyad par rab 'bring tha ma'am mtha' ste
NK071(du)005:1119: de bzhir phye basa yin gyi /
NK071(du)005:1120: 'bras bu thob pa'i ngo bo la khyad par med do //
NK071(du)005:1121: gsum pa bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa de la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:1122: dang po 'bras bu'i ngo bo dngos ni /
NK071(du)005:1123: gong gi sgrub pa mthar phyin pa'i dus der las
NK071(du)005:1124: kyi rnam smin las byung ba'i 'byung bzhi 'dus pa'i
NK071(du)005:1125: lus de nyid rig pa rang snang du gyur nas
NK071(du)005:1126: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i rigs su'am lus su
NK071(du)005:1127: gyur nas tsha la dbang bsgyur rig 'dzin la sbyor
NK071(du)005:1128: nas / 'khor ba dang ngan song las phyir mi ldog pa'i sa la nges par mthar phyin pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1129: gnyis pa tshe dbang gzhan las 'di nyid dpags tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1130: shes rab lta ba rtogs pa dang bsgom pa ting
NK071(du)005:1131: 'dzin dang ldan pa mina pa yi sman gyi tshe
NK071(du)005:1132: dbang dang / sngags kyi tshe dbang dang la sogas pa'i khong du rlung bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1133: thiga le bsgom pa la sogs pa'i sgo nas tshe
NK071(du)005:1134: dbang thob pa lasa 'dir lam mchog rdzogs pa chen
NK071(du)005:1136: gnyis pa de lnga'i skabs las rkyen gyi 'chi ltas byung na 'pho ba bsgom tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1137: 'khor bar ldog pa dang bcas pa tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi dang /
NK071(du)005:1138: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub nyid du skye shi med par
NK071(du)005:1139: rdo rje'i lus su ma grub para 'chi ba'i rkyen
NK071(du)005:1140: gyi las kyis 'byung bzhi'i lus 'jig par gyur na
NK071(du)005:1141: / dbang po drug gi spyod yul la 'gyur ba'i
NK071(du)005:1142: tshe na de ting la sogs pa ranga ranga gi
NK071(du)005:1143: bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor gasla bar byas shing /
NK071(du)005:1144: ting nge 'dzin stobsa che basa sngon gyi las ngan
NK071(du)005:1145: pa'i rgyun gacada pa'i ting 'dzin zin nas 'das na
NK071(du)005:1146: / sngon gsang sngags la mos nas bsgoms pa'i 'brela
NK071(du)005:1147: pa yi stobs kyis bde bar gshegas pa sprul sku
NK071(du)005:1148: 'jig rten du byon nas sngagsa kyi theg pa gsungs
NK071(du)005:1149: pa dang dus gnas bkol bar mi 'gyur te /
NK071(du)005:1150: de'i bstan la zhugs pa'i bshes gnyen dam pa zhal mthong nas /
NK071(du)005:1151: yang dag pa'i mthar lam la sbyor ro //
NK071(du)005:1152: gsum pa lta sgom gnyis kyi skabs la rgyu rkyen
NK071(du)005:1153: 'bras gsum dang ldan zhing re re la'ang dgos ched
NK071(du)005:1154: gnyis gnyis yod cing rim cig char gyi sgo nas
NK071(du)005:1155: 'bras bu la sbyor dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1156: mdor na rgyu shesa pa lta ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1157: rkyen 'jug pa ting 'dzin lnga ste drug la yanga /
NK071(du)005:1158: gnas skabs kyi sgo nas rgyu lta ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1159: rkyen de ting nas spros pa man chad dang /
NK071(du)005:1160: 'bras bu tshogs grub dang gsum la ldan no //
NK071(du)005:1161: rgyu de dang rkyen der dang 'bras bu dera yanga gsum po re re la'ang /
NK071(du)005:1162: gzhan sel dang don gnyer gyi dgos ched gnyis gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1163: blo che chung gi sgo nas 'jug tshul gnyis kyis rang rang gi don la sbyor bar byed do //
NK071(du)005:1164: gnyis pa spyod pa la's gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:1165: dang po spyod pa rgyun gyi tshogs bsags pas gzhan gyi don sgrub tshul mdor bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1166: lta sgom las su rung bar byed pa la spyod
NK071(du)005:1167: pa dus rgyun chad med par spyod lam gyi sgo
NK071(du)005:1168: nas tshogas basgas pa'i phyir rnal 'byor pa bdag don
NK071(du)005:1169: dang gdul bya gzhan don bsgrub par bya ba yi
NK071(du)005:1171: gnyis pa bye brag phye ste de la bshad pa drug /
NK071(du)005:1172: dang po spyod pa'i ngo bo la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1173: dang po gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:1174: bsgrub pa la bdag don du ting nge 'dzin dang
NK071(du)005:1176: bdag don la zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i tshogs lam bzhi dang /
NK071(du)005:1177: zag pa yod la ldog pa med pa sbyor lam
NK071(du)005:1178: nas mthong lam la slob par byed pa'i thabs la
NK071(du)005:1179: spyod par byed pa la yongs su shes par bya
NK071(du)005:1180: ba'i dngos po bcu nyams su blangs shing 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:1182: de'ang tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'i dang po de ting
NK071(du)005:1183: gi skabs su bdag gi don bya ba'i phyir du
NK071(du)005:1184: / bsgom bya sgom byed gnyis mi dmigas pa'i tshul
NK071(du)005:1185: gyis dmigs pa med pa'i ngang la spyod pa dang
NK071(du)005:1186: / / gnyis pa kun ting gi skabs su tshad
NK071(du)005:1187: med pa bzhi yi ngang la rola cing spyod pa
NK071(du)005:1188: / / dang / gsum pa rgya gcig gi skabs
NK071(du)005:1189: su rnal 'byor phyogsa gcig pa ste yi ge nas
NK071(du)005:1190: bzung ste lha dgu nyid bcu'i ngang la 'abda cing
NK071(du)005:1191: / / dang / spyod pa dang / bzhi pa
NK071(du)005:1192: rgya spros la'ang rnal 'byor lha du ma spros pa'i
NK071(du)005:1194: lnga pa tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su spros pa mthar
NK071(du)005:1195: phyin pa'i dus kyi tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i
NK071(du)005:1196: tshogas sgrub pa'i dus su yo byad lnga la rala
NK071(du)005:1198: gnyis pa gzhan don gyi spyod pa byed lugs ni /
NK071(du)005:1199: gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:1200: de ting la sogs pa so so'i rnal 'byor bsgom
NK071(du)005:1201: pa'i dus su gzhan gyi don byed pa ci smos
NK071(du)005:1202: te dang pa de ting skabs nas bzung ste /
NK071(du)005:1203: rgyud don yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po
NK071(du)005:1204: bcu gazhana la ston canga gdul bya lam la bkri
NK071(du)005:1205: bar byed do // gnyis pa lam gyis tshad mtho
NK071(du)005:1206: dman gyis phye bas spyod pa la khyad par yod
NK071(du)005:1208: dang po mos nus kyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1209: lam gong 'og gi spyod pa'i khyad par /
NK071(du)005:1210: de ting kun snang rgya gcig spros dang tshogs sgrub dang lnga la rim pa bzhin du /
NK071(du)005:1211: lam 'og ma rnams kyis lam gong ma rnams kyi spyod pa rnams la mos pas slob cing /
NK071(du)005:1212: lam rang rang gting 'dzina dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dngosa su nus pas spyod la /
NK071(du)005:1213: de'ang phyogs re'i sgo nas bdag don dang gzhan don gnyis ka gang yang spyod pa min la /
NK071(du)005:1214: phyogs med bdag gzhan gnyis ka grol bar bya ba'i don du spyod do //
NK071(du)005:1215: gnyis pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi spyod pa'i khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1216: rang gi ting nge 'dzin dang mthun pa'i ngang la
NK071(du)005:1217: thams cad ma spangs par dbang bsgyur gsang sngags thabas
NK071(du)005:1218: kyi spyod pa tsam du 'dra yanga /
NK071(du)005:1219: rnal 'byor ting 'dzin stobs che chung gi nus mthu yis dbye bas khyad par yod par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)005:1220: gsum pa gzhan don byin rlabs kyi spyod pa la khyad yod tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1221: ting 'dzin la khyad yod pa de bzhin gzhan don byin rlabs phrin las bzhi dang /
NK071(du)005:1222: tshad med bzhi yi sgo nas gdul bya'i blo dang
NK071(du)005:1223: 'atshamas par don mdzad pa'i dus la babs pa'i spyod
NK071(du)005:1224: pa yanga / shes rab lta ba dang sgom pa
NK071(du)005:1225: ting nge 'dzin stobsa che chung rnams kyis phye nas
NK071(du)005:1226: gzhan don rgya che chung yod pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1227: gsum pa spyod yul du rang gi sgo gsum bsdam dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1228: bdag gi don dag gam gzhan gyi don phyir spyod lam bzhi po thams cad du /
NK071(du)005:1229: rnal 'byor lam gyi rim pa mtho dman yod pa
NK071(du)005:1230: bzhin du rang gi lus ngag yid gsum sgo gsum
NK071(du)005:1231: gyi mi dge ba rnams bsdam nas ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)005:1233: bzhi pa tshogs drug gis yul la spyod dus rang
NK071(du)005:1234: grol zhing gzhan mos par byed pa'i thabs la spyod
NK071(du)005:1235: dgos tshul ni / longas spyod kyi rnam pa tshogs
NK071(du)005:1236: drug la spyod pa'i dus su bsgom pa rnal 'byor
NK071(du)005:1237: lam gyi rim pa ting 'dzin rang dang mthun par
NK071(du)005:1238: spyod pas rang rgyud grol zhing gdul bya gzhan rnams
NK071(du)005:1240: lnga pa spyod pa rgyun gyi tshogs gnyis bsags thabs bstan pa la gsum /
NK071(du)005:1241: dang po tshogs gnyis bsags thabs dngos ni /
NK071(du)005:1242: longas spyod thams cad la spyod dus rang rgyud dam
NK071(du)005:1243: sdug bsngal gyi zug rngu med pas bde ba'i rtsal
NK071(du)005:1244: ma 'gags pas bsoda nams kyi tshogs nyid dang /
NK071(du)005:1245: longs spyod pa la zin chags sam 'dzin chags dang brala ba ye shes kyi tshogs yin moda /
NK071(du)005:1246: gnyis pa de lam gyis mtshams gang gi skabs la spyod dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1247: bsod nams kyi tshogs de dang ye shes kyi tshogs
NK071(du)005:1248: de gnyis ka'ang sa chod mtho dman gyis phye ba
NK071(du)005:1249: yi stobs kyis zaga pa dang bcas pa tshogs lam
NK071(du)005:1251: sbyor lam tshogs sgrub kyi bsnyen pa /
NK071(du)005:1253: sgrub pa dang sgrub chen bzhisa tshogs gnyis zung 'jug tu sgrub cing /
NK071(du)005:1254: 'bras bu zag meda kyi rig 'dzin thob thabs la slob ste spyod par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)005:1255: gsum pa nyan bsam sgom pa nas bzung ste rgyud
NK071(du)005:1256: don yongs su shes par bya ba'i dngos po gang
NK071(du)005:1257: nyams su blang ba'i skabs su tshogs gnyis zung 'jug
NK071(du)005:1258: tu ldan dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1259: gzhan yang mnyan pa dang bsam pa dang chos nyid
NK071(du)005:1260: gnas lugs mthonga ba la sogs pa'i spyod pa ma
NK071(du)005:1261: 'gags pa bsoda namas dang ma dmigs pa ye shes
NK071(du)005:1262: kyi tshogs dang / rgyud don gyi dabnga dang dam
NK071(du)005:1263: tshig dang rnal 'byor ting nge 'dzin dang sgrub pa
NK071(du)005:1264: kyi tshogs dang / dang / machada pa dang phrin
NK071(du)005:1265: lasa dang dkyil 'khor dang spyod pa dang sogas kyi
NK071(du)005:1266: sgras sngags dang phyag rgya la spyod pa'i dus kun
NK071(du)005:1267: la'ang bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshagas dang gnyis
NK071(du)005:1269: de'ang ma 'gags par spyod pa bsod nams dang ma
NK071(du)005:1270: dmigs pa'i chagas dang bral ba ye shes kyi tshogs
NK071(du)005:1271: dang gnyis kyi cha yis dbye na dus rgyun du
NK071(du)005:1272: tshogas gnyis bsags pa ni gdod ma thos bsam nas
NK071(du)005:1273: bzung mtha'a 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi bar du tshogs
NK071(du)005:1274: gnyis dang ldan par spyod dgos pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1275: drug pa bdag don gyi spyod pa la gzhan don rdzogs tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1276: badga gi don bya ba'i phyir lta ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1277: rnal 'byor ting 'dzin dang gnyis dbyer med du khyer ba'i grogs spyod pa gal che bas /
NK071(du)005:1278: de'ang spyod lam 'gro nyal 'dug sdod za zhing spyod
NK071(du)005:1279: pa'i dus kun tu spyod pa'i ting 'dzin nyamsa par
NK071(du)005:1280: mi bya ba / de nyid bsgom pa'i thog mar
NK071(du)005:1281: gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir sems bskyed
NK071(du)005:1283: de bas na bdag don du gzhan don bya ba dang rnam pa gnyis rdzogsa pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1284: spyi don gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1285: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin dang /
NK071(du)005:1286: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob tshul bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1288: spyi dang bye brag gnyis su bstan pa las /
NK071(du)005:1289: dang po spyir lta sgom spyod gsum nus mthu can
NK071(du)005:1290: du gyur pas lus yod med kyi sgo nas 'bras
NK071(du)005:1291: bu tshe rnam la sbyor tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1292: lta ba de dang sgom pa de dang spyod pa
NK071(du)005:1293: de dang gsum po yi nus pa mthu cana du
NK071(du)005:1294: gyur nas mthong lam rnam par smin pa dang tshe
NK071(du)005:1295: la dbang bsgyur ba yi rig 'dzin thob lugs kyi
NK071(du)005:1296: lus gnyis su phyi nas bshad pa ni 'di lta
NK071(du)005:1297: ste / de'ang sems las lus lhag pa'am ma lhag
NK071(du)005:1298: pa'i lus yoda pa de nyid ma spangs par lha
NK071(du)005:1299: rtog zung 'jug tu rtogs pa'i tshe dbang dang lhag
NK071(du)005:1300: ma'i lus med pa rnam smin dang gnyis thob tshul
NK071(du)005:1302: zag bcas mthar phyin lam pa'i mthong lam gyi rig 'dzin dngosa la sbyor bar byed /
NK071(du)005:1303: gnyis pa bye brag tu 'bras bu thob tshul de la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:1304: lhag med rnam smin thob tshul dang /
NK071(du)005:1305: lhag bcas tshe dbang thob tshul lo //
NK071(du)005:1306: dang po rnam smin la bzhi ste /
NK071(du)005:1307: dang po rnam smin thob pa'i rgyu ngos bzung ba ni /
NK071(du)005:1308: phyag rgya gcig pa la brtan pa thob pas rnam smin thob nas phyag chen du 'phosa pa yanga /
NK071(du)005:1309: dper na khyung sgong rgya dang seng ge mngal rgya ji lta ba bzhin du thob pa na /
NK071(du)005:1310: phyag rgya spros bcas dang tshagas sgrub kyi skabsa na rnam smin thob pa smos kyang ci dgosa /
NK071(du)005:1311: gnyis pa rnam smin gyi ngo bo dang lam gong ma la sbyor tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1312: yid kyis yi dam gyi lha yi gzugsa la brtan pa thob cinga /
NK071(du)005:1313: phyag rgya lha'i sku de nyid rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba /
NK071(du)005:1314: lus lha gang yin gyi cha lugs su gyur pa na rnam smin no //
NK071(du)005:1315: de nas lhag ma yi lus de nyid bzhag pa'i dus su bar do ma shar ba'i gong la /
NK071(du)005:1316: lhag ma'i lus de med par phyag rgya chen pora smin nas thob pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1317: gsum pa rnam smin gyi nges tshig ni /
NK071(du)005:1318: sngon gyi las kyi lus kyi sbubs su snang ba'i rnam pa /
NK071(du)005:1319: yid yi dam gyi lha yi rnal 'byor du smin pas na /
NK071(du)005:1320: 'bras bu phyag chen thob pa la ma dag pa'i cha la rnam smin du minga btagsa pa ste /
NK071(du)005:1321: smin pa'i 'bras bu ye shesa kyi lus phyag rgya chen po'i cha lugs su 'grub bo //
NK071(du)005:1322: bzhi pa dgongs spyod ni thob pa rang dang khyad par med tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1323: dper na rgya miga tu rgya sa lta bu'i rnam smin thob pa'i tsha na /
NK071(du)005:1324: dgongas pa dang spyod pa ni 'gyur sa ste sngar thob pa'i phyag rgya gcig pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1326: tshogs sgrub gsum la 'drar spyod pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1327: gnyis pa tshe dbang la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1328: dang po tshe dbang thob pa'i rgyu dang rang sa'i yul bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1329: sngon rnam smin bzhin du tshogs sgrub kyi 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:1330: tshe la dbang bsgyur pa'i riga 'dzin nyid du sbyor
NK071(du)005:1331: ba yin te / de nas de nyid kyi thog
NK071(du)005:1332: nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu grub pa yi yun
NK071(du)005:1333: ba yin te / ni / gdul bya gzhan gyi
NK071(du)005:1334: don bya ba'i phyir yun bskal bar gnas mod kyang
NK071(du)005:1335: ba yin te / ni / / bdag gi don
NK071(du)005:1336: bya ba'i phyir brgya phrag bcu drug ste chig stong
NK071(du)005:1337: drug brgya tshun chad du yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i
NK071(du)005:1338: sku lnga lhun grub thob bo //
NK071(du)005:1339: gnyis pa lam gong ma lam sbyor tshul la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1340: tshogs sbyor la lha bsam yas lhun grub bsgom zhing
NK071(du)005:1341: 'dir mthong ba'i stobs kyis thod rgal la sbyor tshul
NK071(du)005:1342: dang / de ma gsal ba'i skyon gyis mthar chags su sbyor tshul lo //
NK071(du)005:1344: dang po thod rgal du 'gro ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK071(du)005:1345: tshe dbang thob pa de yi tshe bsam yas lhun
NK071(du)005:1346: grub kyi ting 'dzin la mnga' brnyes pa yin te
NK071(du)005:1348: tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su bsgomsa shing bsgrubs pas /
NK071(du)005:1349: 'dir mnyam rjes med par mngon sum du mthonga ba'i
NK071(du)005:1350: stobsa kyis 'jig pa lnga dang bral ba yin te
NK071(du)005:1352: 'tsho ba med pa'i dang mis mi basngagasa pa dang 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal dang //
NK071(du)005:1353: 'khor gyi 'dri ba'i 'jigs bral 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa med pa lnga /
NK071(du)005:1357: gnyis pa thod rgal dngos de la gsum /
