NK071(du)005:1358: dang po tshe dbang nas lhun grub thob tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1359: de'ang zag med kyi rgyu shes pa lta ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1360: rkyen 'jug pa ting 'dzin gnyis dus gcig tu brtan
NK071(du)005:1361: pa thob pa'i rgyu rkyen gyi stobs kyis rgyal tshab
NK071(du)005:1362: kyi skyes bu lhun grub rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK071(du)005:1363: de'i tshe rgyal ba drug pa'i zhal mngon sum mthonga
NK071(du)005:1364: nasa rang don nas gnyis med zung 'jug gi sku
NK071(du)005:1365: lnga yongs su rdzogsa pa sa lam mthar phyin nas
NK071(du)005:1366: lhag ma'i lus de skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i
NK071(du)005:1367: lus su smin pa yin te /
NK071(du)005:1368: de'ang sngar gyi lhag ma'i lus de nyid spang ba
NK071(du)005:1369: med par ye shes kyi sku lus nyid du lhun
NK071(du)005:1370: gyis 'grub cing / gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyira smin pa longs sku dang /
NK071(du)005:1371: de nyid du mar 'char ba sprul pa'i sku lus
NK071(du)005:1372: nyid thob pa de nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:1373: yi ge 'khor lo tshogas chen gyi sa la sbyor
NK071(du)005:1374: ba yin no // de ni rig 'dzin gsum spyir
NK071(du)005:1375: thob lugs kyi sgo nas sangs rgyas kyi sar sbyor
NK071(du)005:1377: gnyis pa tshe dbang rang gis sangs rgyas grub tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1378: blo che ba cig char ba kha cig tshe la
NK071(du)005:1379: dbang bsgyur ba'i riga 'dzin pa de nyid kyi sa
NK071(du)005:1380: nasa lo brgya phrag bcu drug gi rgyun gyi tha
NK071(du)005:1381: mar ston pa gsang ba'i skus dbang bskur nas bag
NK071(du)005:1382: nyal gyi dri ma dag ste sku lnga lhun grub
NK071(du)005:1383: tu rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas thob bo //
NK071(du)005:1384: gsum pa tshe dbang phyag chen la sbyor nas de nas sangs rgyas grub tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1385: thod rgal ba kha ciga tshe dbang thob nas phyag rgya chen po yi rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK071(du)005:1386: de nasa dbang thob pa dang 'bras bu bla na
NK071(du)005:1387: meda pa spyod yul thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK071(du)005:1388: su yongs su dag pa kun tu bazanga pora thob
NK071(du)005:1389: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa mthar chags pas mthong
NK071(du)005:1390: lam tshe dbang bsgom lam phyag chen mthar lam lhun
NK071(du)005:1391: grub kyi rig 'dzin nam sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul
NK071(du)005:1392: par 'gyur ro // la bcu ste / dang po
NK071(du)005:1393: mtshon pa dpe'i khyad par bstan pa'i sgo nas lam
NK071(du)005:1398: mthar thug pa'i rina chana dang bzhi yi 'od rgya mtsho la phog pas /
NK071(du)005:1399: rin chen nyi 'od kyis zho ru 'gyur ba ltar /
NK071(du)005:1400: zag bcas kyi nyon mongs pa de nyid zag med kyi ye shes su 'gyur la /
NK071(du)005:1401: bsgom lam phyag chen rig 'dzin thob pa'i dus su /
NK071(du)005:1402: de bas kyang stobs su zhugs te /
NK071(du)005:1403: rin chen rlan med pa'i 'od phog pas mar du 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK071(du)005:1404: mthong lam du da dung kun 'gro'i sgrib pa yod de /
NK071(du)005:1405: 'dir ye shes su shar nas lus sems rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1406: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi skabs su de bas kyang stobs su gyur te /
NK071(du)005:1407: rin chen med 'od phog pas me yi rnam par 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK071(du)005:1408: bsgom lam la lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma yod pa de /
NK071(du)005:1409: 'dir ye shes su shar nas sku lnga lhun grub rig 'dzin du 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)005:1410: mthar thug gi dus su de bas kyang stobs su gyur te /
NK071(du)005:1411: mthar thug pa'i nor bu'i 'od phog nas thams cad
NK071(du)005:1412: stong zhing ma lus pa'i snang bar byed pa ltar
NK071(du)005:1413: du / mthar lam pa'i bag nyal gyi dri ma
NK071(du)005:1414: sa bon dang bcas pa spangs nas ye shes chen
NK071(du)005:1415: po'i rang bzhin gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1417: kye rgyal ba'i sras po dag /
NK071(du)005:1418: rgya mtsho chen por 'dus pa'i chu yi phung po de dag kyang /
NK071(du)005:1419: nor bu nyi ma'i 'od phog chu yi rang bzhin
NK071(du)005:1420: spangs nas 'o ma dang zho ru gyur te 'dug
NK071(du)005:1421: go // nor bu rin po che rlan med pa'i
NK071(du)005:1422: 'od phog na 'o ma dang zho'i rang bzhin spangs
NK071(du)005:1423: go // nas / mar gyi nying khu lta bur 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)005:1424: me'i 'od kyi nor bu rin po che'i 'od phog
NK071(du)005:1425: na mar gyi nying khu lta bu'i rang bzhin spangs
NK071(du)005:1426: te / me ltar bur 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)005:1427: nor bu rin po che ma lus pa mthar thug
NK071(du)005:1428: pa'i 'od phog na thams cad lhag ma med cing
NK071(du)005:1429: ma lus pa'i snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)005:1431: gnyis pa bgrod pa lam gyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1432: rim pa pa kha cig mthong lam tshe dbang dang /
NK071(du)005:1434: mthar lam lhun grub rnam pa gsum bgrod cing sbyangs
NK071(du)005:1435: pa'i stobs kyis mathara lhun grub riga 'dzin dbang thob
NK071(du)005:1436: pa las yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i sangas rgyas sku
NK071(du)005:1438: gsum pa btags pa ming don gyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1439: shes rab lta bas dbang po sgo lnga gnyis med
NK071(du)005:1440: rang snang du rtogs shing rnal 'byor ting 'dzin dang
NK071(du)005:1442: gzhi gciga kyang bogs 'don slob pa'i khyad par bsam yas pa rnams la ni /
NK071(du)005:1443: rnal 'byor lta sgom gyi bogas 'don la che chung
NK071(du)005:1444: gi byed las kyi skabsa kyis rig 'dzin gsum gyi
NK071(du)005:1446: de'ang 'khor ba la phyir mi ldog pa mthong lam tshe dbang /
NK071(du)005:1447: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid la mi g.yo ba bsgom lam phyag chen /
NK071(du)005:1448: de nyid mthar phyin pa lhun grub rig 'dzin dang gsum gyis phye ba'am /
NK071(du)005:1449: yang na tshe dbang gi lam lta ba kun sngon
NK071(du)005:1450: du 'gro ba ltar lta ba rtogs pas 'jigas pa
NK071(du)005:1452: phyag chen gyis nyi khri bzhi stong la sogs snang
NK071(du)005:1453: ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin yongas su rdzogs
NK071(du)005:1454: pa dang / lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis rang rig
NK071(du)005:1455: pa'i ngang la dga' ba bcu drug la ye shes
NK071(du)005:1456: lnga lnga'i rtsal rdzogsa pas mtha' ma'i mthar thug gi
NK071(du)005:1457: 'bras bu'i sar sbyor bas na sbyor lam pa zhes
NK071(du)005:1458: pa dang / bya'o // bzhi pa dag bya sgrib pa'i khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1459: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi don dang gdul bya gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir na'ang /
NK071(du)005:1464: ngag barlanga po ste spyod pa lnga /
NK071(du)005:1465: byams snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms te tshad meda
NK071(du)005:1466: pa bzhi la sogas pa'i sgras phrin las bzhi dang
NK071(du)005:1467: / de ltar dag ma dag gi spyod pa rnamas
NK071(du)005:1468: gnyis med rang snang gi ngang las ma g.yos par
NK071(du)005:1469: / spyod pas / bzang ngan rang kha ma'i dri
NK071(du)005:1470: mas mi gos pa la 'dra moda kyang khyad par
NK071(du)005:1471: / spyod pas / yod de / de'ang mthong lam
NK071(du)005:1472: la lta ba kun tu 'gro ba rtogs pa'i don
NK071(du)005:1473: la ma g.yengs par bsgom pa des phyag chen gyi
NK071(du)005:1475: bsgom lam la bzhi khri bzhi stong gi thog tu gnas pa'i tshe /
NK071(du)005:1476: de las gzhan pa'i rtsal du ma dang /
NK071(du)005:1477: lhun grub kyi dgongs pa sgrib pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1478: mthar lam dus su ye shes lnga lnga'i rtsal dang ldan pa la /
NK071(du)005:1479: bag la nyal gyi dri ma se gol brdab pa'i
NK071(du)005:1480: yun tsam zhig gi sgrib pa dang gsum ni lam
NK071(du)005:1481: gonga 'og gi mtho dman gyi cha yisa phye bas
NK071(du)005:1482: / lam gong ma gong mar phyin pa'i dus 'og ma 'og ma'i sgrib pa dag pa'i phyir na /
NK071(du)005:1483: rig 'dzin gsum po da dag gi dgongs pa nyid
NK071(du)005:1484: kyi lam la khyad para yod pa de ltar 'gyur
NK071(du)005:1485: ro // lnga pa dgongs pa yul nus kyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1486: gzhan don gdul bya'i yul dang rang don dgongs pa
NK071(du)005:1487: ting 'dzin gyi nus pa la'ang mtho dman gyi khyad
NK071(du)005:1488: par yada de gang zhe na 'og nas 'byung ba
NK071(du)005:1489: 'di lta ste / drug pa mngon shes yul sogs kyi khyad par la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:1490: dang po rig 'dzin gsum gyi mngon shes spyod pa
NK071(du)005:1491: cho 'phrul bzhi thob pa tsam 'dra bar bstan pa
NK071(du)005:1492: ni / gong du ngos bzung ba de bzhin du khyad par /
NK071(du)005:1493: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad na rig 'dzin gsum gyi
NK071(du)005:1494: skabs su lha'i spyan gyis stong gsum brgya la sogs
NK071(du)005:1495: pa'i gzugs che chung nye ring med par mngon sum
NK071(du)005:1496: du mkhyen pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1497: de bzhin du lha'i rna ba'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1498: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1499: sems can pha rol po rnams kyi sems rgyud thams cad shes pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1500: sems can rnams kyi 'chi 'pho dang skye ba mkhyen pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1501: rdzu 'phrul gyi bya ba mi mthun pa brgyad la
NK071(du)005:1502: sogs pa'i mngona par shes pa dang drug brtsi nas
NK071(du)005:1503: / zag zad la mngon par shes pa spyir btang ba'am /
NK071(du)005:1504: yang na rdzu 'phrul spyir btang nas zag pa zad pa'i mngon par shes pa drug dang /
NK071(du)005:1505: bdag don dang gzhan don gyi spyod pa yisa don gnyis byed lugs dang /
NK071(du)005:1509: kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul dang bzhi ste rnam grangs de dag dang 'drara dbang thob moda kyang /
NK071(du)005:1512: byin rlabs rnams la khyad yod tshul /
NK071(du)005:1513: rig 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyi mngon shes kyi yul dang /
NK071(du)005:1515: thugs rje byin rlabsa la sogas pa rnams la rgya che chung gi khyad par yod par 'gyur te /
NK071(du)005:1516: de'ang tshe dbang gis stong gsum gcig la gling bzhi
NK071(du)005:1517: bye ba phrag bargya'am stong gsum gyi 'jig rten khams
NK071(du)005:1518: brgya'i yul dang zhing khams mkhyen zhing /
NK071(du)005:1519: lha mi'i rgyal po'i cha byad kyis sems can gyi don byed pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1520: phyag chen gyis stong gsum gyi 'jig rten gyi khams
NK071(du)005:1521: brgya gcig nas gnyis su bgrang ba'i stong phrag bcu'i
NK071(du)005:1522: 'jig rten gyi khams rdul snyed du byas pa grangs
NK071(du)005:1523: de rnyed dang mnyam pa'i rgya de gcig nas gnyis
NK071(du)005:1524: su bgrangs pa'i stong phrag bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK071(du)005:1525: rdul snyed kyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i zhing khams su
NK071(du)005:1526: rtsa ba'i lus las mi g.yo ba'i ngang nas sprul
NK071(du)005:1527: pa'i lus rngon pa dang smad 'tshong ma la sogs
NK071(du)005:1528: kyi sgo nas sems can gyi don byed pa dang
NK071(du)005:1529: / lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi mngon shes kyis yul
NK071(du)005:1530: dang gdul bya tshad bzung med pa'i zhing khams la
NK071(du)005:1531: / / rtsa lus lhun grub las ma g.yos par
NK071(du)005:1532: sprul pa mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis sems can gyi
NK071(du)005:1533: / / don byed pa'o // bdun pa bogs 'don spyod pa'i khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1534: 'o na bdag don la khyad par med dam zhe na ma yin te /
NK071(du)005:1535: rig 'dzin gsum gyis bdag gi don bya ba'i phyir spyod pa dgos te /
NK071(du)005:1536: de'ang tshe dbang gis gong bzhin bzang ngan gyi dngos
NK071(du)005:1537: po gang la'ang yongas su ma chagas pa rig pa
NK071(du)005:1538: rang snang gi ngang la spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1539: phyag chen gyi dgong pa shin tu mi g.yo ba'i rnal 'byor ting 'dzin gyi spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1540: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyi dgongs pa rang byung gi
NK071(du)005:1541: ye shes kyi rtsala gyis ye shes brgya bcu'i ting
NK071(du)005:1542: 'dzin gyi ngang las mi 'da' bar spyod pa yisa
NK071(du)005:1543: / de ltar bdag don gyi spyood pa de'i yon tan gyis /
NK071(du)005:1544: rang lam 'og ma nas gong ma'i don rnamas la yongas su gong nas gong du 'phar barbyed pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1545: brgyad pa mdo sngags sa lam gyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)005:1546: rig 'dzin gsum po de yang mdo'i sa lam dang brang sprad cing khyad par dbye ba /
NK071(du)005:1547: sngags kyi dang po mthong lam tshe dbang dang mtshan
NK071(du)005:1548: nyid kyi dang po rab tu dga' ba gnyis mthong
NK071(du)005:1549: lam tsam dang skal ba mnyam pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1550: gnyis pa'i phyag rgya chen po'i riga 'dzin mchoga de dang /
NK071(du)005:1551: mtshan nyid kyi sa brgyad pa'i byang chub semas dapara
NK071(du)005:1552: zhes sems dpa' gnyis bsgom lam yin par skal ba
NK071(du)005:1553: manyama mo // gsum pa lhun grub rig 'dzin dang /
NK071(du)005:1555: mthar lam gyi sgra tsam dang skal ba mnyam moda kyang /
NK071(du)005:1556: don gyis khyad par yod de gang zhe na /
NK071(du)005:1557: lus snang sems zung 'jug gam bden gsum dbyer med
NK071(du)005:1558: du rtogs na bsgom pa'i dgongas pa rgya mtsho dang
NK071(du)005:1559: / spang blang dgag sgrub med pa'i spyod pa rgya
NK071(du)005:1560: mtshosa 'og ma las khyad para 'aphagas pa yin te
NK071(du)005:1561: / / de'i rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK071(du)005:1562: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i lta ba stong pa'i thog tu dmigs pa de /
NK071(du)005:1563: gsang sngags zung 'jug gi lta ba'i sgrib pa yin pasa khyad de ltar phye ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)005:1564: dgu pa mdzad pa cho 'phrul gyi khyad par la gnyis /
NK071(du)005:1565: dang po rig 'dzin gsum gyi mdzad pa cho 'phrul la khyad par yod tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1566: mthonga lam tshe dbang rig 'dzin pasa gong ma gnyis
NK071(du)005:1567: la ltos na ched du rtsol ba'i rnam pa tsam
NK071(du)005:1568: gyis cha 'phrul bzhi la sogs pa rnams ston pa
NK071(du)005:1569: dang / phyag chen rnal 'byor dgongs pa ting 'dzin
NK071(du)005:1570: las mi g.yo bzhin du cho 'phrul bzhi'i rnam pa
NK071(du)005:1572: lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis 'bad pa dang brtsal ba med par cho 'phrul bzhi la sogs madzada pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1573: de ltar tshe dbang de dang /
NK071(du)005:1575: lhun grub da gsum ni lta sgom spyod gsum la
NK071(du)005:1576: brtan pa thob che chung gi cha yasa phye ba
NK071(du)005:1577: yina no // gnyis pa lhun grub kyi mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1578: de dag mtha'a ru phyin pa'i lam la lhun gyis
NK071(du)005:1579: grub pa mi rig 'dzin de rgyal ba drug pa'i
NK071(du)005:1580: rgyal tshab kyi skyes bu madzada nas /
NK071(du)005:1581: phyag chen man chad la gsang ba'i chos bla na med ba'i 'khor lo yang daga par bskor zhing /
NK071(du)005:1582: gdul bya kun la mthun pa dang phan gdags pa'i
NK071(du)005:1583: phyir gang 'dul gyi gzugs sku sna tshogs ston cinga
NK071(du)005:1585: yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa /
NK071(du)005:1591: byang chub shing drung gshegs pa /
NK071(du)005:1596: sku gdung cha brgyad du bgos pa ste /
NK071(du)005:1597: madzada pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas chos kyang ston pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1598: 'khor ba spyi dang bye brag gi sdug bsngal las
NK071(du)005:1599: so sor thar bar byed pa'i thabs nyan thos la
NK071(du)005:1600: sogs pa'i lam yang ston pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1601: gzhan yang gang la gang 'dul gyi phrin las rnams
NK071(du)005:1602: kyis sems can thams cad kun gyi don byas pa
NK071(du)005:1603: rdzogs nas mthar skye shi med pa'i chos sku 'gyur
NK071(du)005:1604: ba med pa'i g.yung drung thaba pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1605: bcu pa slob dpon gyi khyad par bstan pa'i sgo nas lam bgrod tshul bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1606: gong du bshad pa'i gtan tshigs de bas na nus
NK071(du)005:1607: pa mthu can du gyur pa'i rig 'dzin rnam pa
NK071(du)005:1608: gsum po yi slob dpon ni 'di lta ste /
NK071(du)005:1609: de'ang tshe dbang gi slob dpon sprul pa yi sku dang /
NK071(du)005:1610: phyag chen gyi slob dpon longas spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK071(du)005:1611: lhun grub kyi slob dpon ni rgyal ba drug pa
NK071(du)005:1612: chos kyi sku dang gsum la rima para sku'i zhal
NK071(du)005:1613: mthonga gsung chos nyan mod kyang rig 'dzin gsum pa
NK071(du)005:1614: ni lta sgom gyi goms pa che chung gi stobs
NK071(du)005:1615: kyis 'og ma gciga gi ston para gong ma gciga
NK071(du)005:1616: gyur pasa na / de dag rim pa bzhin du
NK071(du)005:1617: 'og ma pas gong ma'i bla ma ste blar gyur
NK071(du)005:1618: gyur pasa na / pa yin te / rig 'dzin
NK071(du)005:1619: gsum la mtho dman gyi khyad par che ba de
NK071(du)005:1620: ltar yod pa yin yanga da rung rig 'dzin de
NK071(du)005:1621: dang sangs rgyas kyi sa khyad phye ba ni /
NK071(du)005:1622: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:1623: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1624: cig char ba tshe dbang dang /
NK071(du)005:1625: thod rgal ba phyag chen dang /
NK071(du)005:1626: mthar phyin pa lhun grub dang gsum gyi skabsa nas
NK071(du)005:1627: yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga lhun
NK071(du)005:1628: grub tu gyur pa la yanga /
NK071(du)005:1629: sangs rgyas thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK071(du)005:1630: thob pa'i rkyen dgos pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1631: thob pa'i dgongas pa rang gi ngo bo dang gsum gyi dbang du phye ba yin gyis /
NK071(du)005:1632: sangs rgyas thob pa la khyad para meda par snang
NK071(du)005:1633: ba des na rig 'dzin gsum po de dag gi
NK071(du)005:1634: skabs na sangs rgyas pa la bzang ngan med par
NK071(du)005:1635: kun 'dra yanga gong gi rig 'dzin rang skabs su
NK071(du)005:1636: khyad par yod pa de yi phyir 'dir sangs rgyas
NK071(du)005:1637: la mnyam rjes med pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1638: rig 'dzin la mnyam rjes yod pa de dag mnyam
NK071(du)005:1639: par blta ba ni ma yana te khyad par yod
NK071(du)005:1640: do // gnyis pa bye brag rgyas par bshad pa de la gsum /
NK071(du)005:1641: sangs rgyas pa rang gi rgyu bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1642: sangs rgyas par byed pa'i rkyen dgos par bstan pa /
NK071(du)005:1643: sangs rgyas zin gyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1645: dang po rig 'dzin gsum gang nas sangs rgyas pa
NK071(du)005:1646: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor du ye shes
NK071(du)005:1647: kyi phyag rgya mo la brten nas gsang ba'i sku'i
NK071(du)005:1649: gong du bshad pa de ltar rig 'dzin rnam pa gsum gang zhig thob ba la /
NK071(du)005:1650: shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa yi sangs rgyas mngona sum du byas pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:1651: rang bzhin mthar phyin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor rang rig pa mngon sum du gsal ba'i ngang nas /
NK071(du)005:1652: gzungs ma ye shes kyi lha mora rola cing spyod
NK071(du)005:1653: pa'i dabnga gisa chags rtog thams cad bde ba'i ye
NK071(du)005:1654: shes kyis zil gyis gnon pa seng ge lta bu'i
NK071(du)005:1655: gsang ba'i sku'i gsung go brda' mjal basa bde ba'i
NK071(du)005:1656: dngos po yi ngo bo de ka rgyu rkyen bcos
NK071(du)005:1657: slad dang bral ba'i rang byung bde stong gnyis med
NK071(du)005:1658: kyi ye shes nyams su myong ba'o //
NK071(du)005:1659: gnyis pa de dus sku gsung thugs bco lnga lhun grub tu rdzogs tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1660: sku lnga'am rigs lnga dbyer med pas rdo rje 'dzina
NK071(du)005:1661: pa'i sku drug pa spyi gzugs cana gyi sku lnga
NK071(du)005:1662: gsung lnga thugsa lnga ste lnga gsum bco lnga lhun
NK071(du)005:1663: grub tu rdzogs pa yi don brda' 'phrod pa desa
NK071(du)005:1664: / de'ang ston pa sku lnga'i byin rlabsa 'khor mthar lam pa byang sems 'byin pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1665: gsung lnga'i don dgongs pa ye shes lnga bstan pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:1666: sku gsung thugs kyi lnga tshan gsum kun gyis don lhun grub tu bstan para zada do //
NK071(du)005:1667: gnyis pa sangs rgyas par byed pa'i rkyen dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1668: gong du bshad pa de ltar bstan pa'i phyir mthar
NK071(du)005:1669: lam pa la rjes shes nyon mongs pa gnas ngan
NK071(du)005:1670: len gyi dri ma kun gzhi'i rnam shes gnas cha
NK071(du)005:1671: phra mo tsam zhig yod pa de se gol brdab
NK071(du)005:1672: pa'i yun tsam cig la sgrib pa nyon mongs bag
NK071(du)005:1673: la nyal dang / de'i gnyen po rang byung ye shes rtsal ma yengs par /
NK071(du)005:1674: sgom pa'i rtsol ba la shes bya bag nyal gnyis
NK071(du)005:1675: kyis 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la
NK071(du)005:1676: bsgribs pas mun pa rnam pa gnyis po spang bya
NK071(du)005:1677: yin pas so // rnal 'byor pa rang gi don
NK071(du)005:1678: rang byung gi ye shes nyid la ye shes lnga
NK071(du)005:1679: lnga'i rtsal dang ldan pa'i ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i stobsa
NK071(du)005:1680: dang ni gzhan rkyen ston pas zab mo'i dbang gsum
NK071(du)005:1681: rama pa ltar bskur nas thob pa'i stobsa kyis bdud
NK071(du)005:1682: bzhi bcoma par byas pasa sgrib gnyis sangs te mthar
NK071(du)005:1683: thug gi sangs rgyas kyi sa thob pa'i phyir ye
NK071(du)005:1684: shes phyogsa re'i mtha' dang bral bar ldan pa'i rgyas
NK071(du)005:1685: yin pas so // zhes bya'o // gsum pa dgongs pa'i ngo bo bstan pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)005:1686: mngon du gyur pa'i dgongs pa'i ngo bo bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1687: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo gcig tshul dang /
NK071(du)005:1688: mi gcig par 'dod pa'i gzhan lugs dgag pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1689: rang lugs kyi sangs rgyas kyi mtshan nyid rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1691: dang po 'bras bu mngon du gyur tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1692: dbyer med lhun grub tu rgyal ba drug par sangs rgyas pa de'i tshe na /
NK071(du)005:1693: ma 'dres snang mdzad kyi 'bras bu la /
NK071(du)005:1698: mngon byang sku dang sku lnga /
NK071(du)005:1702: grags stong dbyer med kyi gsung /
NK071(du)005:1703: rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung lnga /
NK071(du)005:1708: me long lta bu'i ye shes te thugsa lnga dang /
NK071(du)005:1713: gdan khri ste yona tan lnga /
NK071(du)005:1714: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin lasa
NK071(du)005:1715: lnga ste ngo matshara rmad du byung ba 'bras bu
NK071(du)005:1716: yi che yon sku rigs rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi
NK071(du)005:1717: shu rtsa lnga po rnams gzhan logs shig la yod
NK071(du)005:1719: 'o na de dag gang las byung zhe na /
NK071(du)005:1720: gzhi ye gdod ma nyid nas 'bras bu'i che yon
NK071(du)005:1721: rang la gnas pa de lam gyi thabas 'gag pa
NK071(du)005:1722: med pa la brten pa'i dus su shes rab rang
NK071(du)005:1723: bzhin med pa nyid las ma g.yos /
NK071(du)005:1724: de ltar thabs shes dbyer med de nyid mthar phyin pa de la 'bras bu zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)005:1725: dper na yid bzhin nor bu dang dpag bsam shing
NK071(du)005:1726: dgos 'dod 'byung ba de lta bu yi 'bras bu'i
NK071(du)005:1727: yon tan rnams rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i ngang
NK071(du)005:1728: du rang la 'byung nas thob pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1729: gnyis pa de'i yon tan gyi cha las mthar phyin gyi sa gsum rdzogs tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1730: bsgom pa'i spyod yul blo yi rtsol ba dang brala
NK071(du)005:1731: basa na gang la'ang ma chagas par thams cad rig
NK071(du)005:1732: pa rang snang rtsol med du shar ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:1733: dper na chu skyes te pad+ma 'dam las skyes kyang
NK071(du)005:1734: 'dam skyon gyis ma gos pa ltar thams cad rang
NK071(du)005:1735: rig ngang la 'dzin zhen chags gsum gyi dri ma
NK071(du)005:1736: dang bral bas na bcu gnyis pad+ma can gyi sa
NK071(du)005:1737: yang thoba pa'o // phung po lnga la sogas rtog
NK071(du)005:1738: tshogs zhe gnyis rang bzhin rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa
NK071(du)005:1740: de nyid rang rig pa'i mngona sum du byas pa'i
NK071(du)005:1741: cha nas bcu gsum yi ge tshogs chen gyi sa
NK071(du)005:1743: sku dang ye shes de nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral
NK071(du)005:1744: bas rang byung gi ye shes su 'od gasla ba
NK071(du)005:1745: yi don de nyid rang rig pa'i mangna sum du
NK071(du)005:1747: bcu bzhi pa ye shes bla ma yi sa thob pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1748: gnyis pa dgongs pa'i ngo bo gcig tshul la drug ste /
NK071(du)005:1749: dang po de bzhin nyid du gshegs tshul gcig tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1750: mthar thug pa gsum mngon du gyur pa'i tshe /
NK071(du)005:1751: rnal ma don gyi kun gzhi ma bcos pa rang rig pa'i mangna du byas pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)005:1752: de ltar gzhi don da bzhin nyid du nar son cing gshegas pa de yanga /
NK071(du)005:1753: rigs drug gi 'agro ba'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK071(du)005:1754: sems rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rgyud tha dad kyang
NK071(du)005:1755: rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i ngo bo la rigas
NK071(du)005:1756: rgyud phyogs gcig tu grub pa mada pa'i phyir shin
NK071(du)005:1758: gnyis pa dgongs pa ma 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs
NK071(du)005:1759: pas gcig du ma'i mtha' dang bral bar gcig tshul
NK071(du)005:1760: ni / gacaga pu de nyid ngo bo la chos
NK071(du)005:1761: kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogsa pa yin pasa
NK071(du)005:1762: ni / na / thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag nyid
NK071(du)005:1763: sangs rgyas bsam yasa pa bzhugs kyang rang riga pa
NK071(du)005:1764: de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du 'dus pas yongs su
NK071(du)005:1765: ni / na / rdzogs pa / rang rig pa
NK071(du)005:1766: de nyid kyi ngang la shes bya'i chos thabas chena
NK071(du)005:1767: po ma 'dres pa'i bye brag rnams rang gsal ba'i
NK071(du)005:1768: ni / na / rdzogs pa / phyir / sangs
NK071(du)005:1769: rgyas thams cad dgongs pa gcig dang du mar bral
NK071(du)005:1770: ba yin par dgongs pa gciga go //
NK071(du)005:1771: gsum pa sems nyid mtha' bral lhun grub mngon du byas par gcig tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1772: ranga gi semas la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK071(du)005:1773: lhun gyis grub cing snang stong gi mtha' dang bral
NK071(du)005:1774: ba yin te / de nyid gsar du ma yin
NK071(du)005:1775: ye gdod ma nas 'khor 'das sam snang stong gi
NK071(du)005:1776: cha shas gnyis dang bral bas dbyer med pasa don
NK071(du)005:1777: ma 'dres yongas rdzogas kyi snying po de nyid rang
NK071(du)005:1778: rig pa'i mngona sum du byas pa dang 'dra pa'i
NK071(du)005:1779: phyir na sangs rgyas kun yang dgongs pa mtha' bral
NK071(du)005:1780: lhun grub ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gciga pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1781: bzhi pa bzhugs gnas kyi zhing khams gcig tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1782: 'das ma 'ongs da lta ma nges pa'i dus dang
NK071(du)005:1783: bzhi po rnams samas nyid rig par snang ba'i phyir
NK071(du)005:1784: dus bzhi snga phyi rang kha ma'i rgyun dang bral
NK071(du)005:1785: ba'i rang bzhin de la gzung ba'i yul dang 'dzina
NK071(du)005:1786: pa'i sems gnyis dang bral ba'i rang snang gnyis med
NK071(du)005:1788: de bzhin gshegas pa kun gyi bzhugs gansa yin pa de yi phyira na gong gi bzhugs gnas dara /
NK071(du)005:1789: rgyal ba kun kyang dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du dgongs pa gciga par bzhugs so //
NK071(du)005:1790: lnga pa pho brang dkyil 'khor gcig tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1791: rang gi semas nyid ye gdod ma nasa chos sku
NK071(du)005:1792: che zhes chen po de bzhin nyid kyi gnas lugs
NK071(du)005:1793: de nyid rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gyur pa
NK071(du)005:1794: na / che ba'i yon tan dapaga tu mada pa'i
NK071(du)005:1795: sangas rgyas rnams kyi bzhugs gnas kyi pho brang yin
NK071(du)005:1796: na / pa'i phyir / pho brang de na sangs
NK071(du)005:1797: rgyas kyi gtso 'khor kun ma 'dres bar bkod pa'i
NK071(du)005:1798: dkyil 'khor gyi gdan der dgongs pa gcig tu gansa
NK071(du)005:1799: na / pa'i phyir / nas bzhugs so // drug
NK071(du)005:1800: pa gnas gyur gyi rgyal ba gcig tshul de la
NK071(du)005:1801: na / pa'i phyir / nas bzhugs so // gnyis
NK071(du)005:1802: / dang po gnas gyur gyi rgyal ba gcig tshul
NK071(du)005:1803: na / pa'i phyir / nas bzhugs so // gnyis
NK071(du)005:1804: / dngos ni / de ltar thams cad dgongs pa
NK071(du)005:1805: gcig pa'i don ngo ma shes pa'i rgyud drag las
NK071(du)005:1806: kyis 'gro ba'i sems can du skye ba'i dus na
NK071(du)005:1807: rigs rgyud lha lha min mi dang dmyal ba yi
NK071(du)005:1808: dwags dud 'gro drug tu snang ba nyid /
NK071(du)005:1809: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo bo la 'gro ba rigas drug rigs rgyud dang /
NK071(du)005:1810: pho mo ma ning gi matshana ma dang gzugs kyi
NK071(du)005:1811: dbyibs kha dog dang ris te nang tshan mi 'dra
NK071(du)005:1812: ba'i dngos po rnams rang rgyud can du grub pa
NK071(du)005:1813: mada pa de yanga ngo bo la tha dad med
NK071(du)005:1814: pa de yi phyir rgyal ba sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK071(du)005:1815: pa'i rgyud la rtog tshogs zhe gnyis rgyal ba bzhi
NK071(du)005:1816: bcu rtsa gnyis la tha dad du gnas su 'gyur
NK071(du)005:1817: ba dang / rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyang ye shes
NK071(du)005:1818: lngar so sor gnas su 'gyur ba'i phyogs dang ris
NK071(du)005:1819: su chad pa'i cha gzung du ga la yada de
NK071(du)005:1820: ba dang / med do // gnyis pa gcig na
NK071(du)005:1821: gnas 'gyur rdzun par dogs pa skye ba bsal ba
NK071(du)005:1823: dang po dogs pa skye tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1824: 'on te gong du bshad pa ltar ma shes pa'i
NK071(du)005:1825: gang zag rnams kyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs
NK071(du)005:1826: pa stong pa'i ngang du chu la chu thim pa
NK071(du)005:1828: 'o na bka' mdo rgyud thams cad kyi nang rtog tshogs lhar gnas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1829: tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar gnas gyur par gsungs pa
NK071(du)005:1830: thams cad rdzun zhing stong pa'i phyogs gcig pa'i mthar
NK071(du)005:1831: ltung zhing dbu ma'i 'bras bu dang 'dra bar 'gyur
NK071(du)005:1832: ba'i dogas pa skye basa de'ang bsal ba 'di ltar
NK071(du)005:1833: te / gnyis pa de bsal ba de la gsum ste /
NK071(du)005:1834: dang po sems 'di 'khor 'das kun kyi dngos gzhi
NK071(du)005:1835: ru snang yang 'khor 'das phyogs ris su ma chad
NK071(du)005:1837: gzhi don kun gzhi byang chub kyi semas de nyid
NK071(du)005:1838: ye gdod ma nyid nas rgyu rkyen dang bral ba
NK071(du)005:1839: rang byung gi ye shes la 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)005:1840: kun lhun grub tu rdzogs par gnas kyang /
NK071(du)005:1841: 'khor 'das kyi snang stong phyogs re'i mtshan nyid mtha'
NK071(du)005:1842: dang bral bas na gsar du mtha' bkol du med
NK071(du)005:1843: pa'i don ni 'khor ba dang mya ngana las 'das
NK071(du)005:1844: pa'i chos kun gyi dangsa gzhi yin te /
NK071(du)005:1845: de nyid ngag tu smra ba'i tshig dang yid kyis bsam pa'i blo dang brala bas /
NK071(du)005:1846: 'khor 'das snang stong phyogs gcig 'di 'drara ngos bzung du meda do //
NK071(du)005:1847: gnyis pa de gnas su 'gyur ba'i ye shes lnga'ang
NK071(du)005:1848: rang byung gi ye shes kyi yon tan gyi cha
NK071(du)005:1854: bya grub ye shes dang lnga yang don rang byung
NK071(du)005:1855: gi ye shes kyi yon tan gyi byed las kyi
NK071(du)005:1856: cha lnga las ye shes lnga'i ming btagsa pa yin
NK071(du)005:1857: par shes dgos kyi de bas logs sam gzhan pa
NK071(du)005:1858: zhig na ye shes lnga meda pa de yi phyir
NK071(du)005:1859: na dbu ma ltar stong pa phyogs gcig pa'i grub
NK071(du)005:1861: gsum pa de na gnas 'gyur gyi rgyal ba'ang mthar
NK071(du)005:1862: lam pa'am rigs lnga la ris yod kyang yang dag
NK071(du)005:1863: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug pa la lhun gyis
NK071(du)005:1865: rang byung gi ye shes kyi rang mdangs kyi rgyal
NK071(du)005:1866: ba drug pa de nyid yid bzhin nor bu rin
NK071(du)005:1868: rgyal ba kun bzang ni zhi khro'i sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs can yin pa'i phyir na /
NK071(du)005:1869: drug pa'i rgyal tshab mthar lam ba la rigs lnga
NK071(du)005:1870: re re la yang gtso 'khor lhun gyis grub pas
NK071(du)005:1872: yang na drug pa'i rgyal tshab rgyal ba rigs lnga
NK071(du)005:1873: po rnam gdul bya'i snang ngo la rigs dang sku
NK071(du)005:1874: mdog zhal phyag mi 'dra ba'i rigs tha dad yod
NK071(du)005:1875: kyi yang dag par rdzogsa pa'i sangas rgyas rigs lnga
NK071(du)005:1876: lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyal ba drug pa la de
NK071(du)005:1877: ltar gyi phyogs ris su grub pa mada do //
NK071(du)005:1878: gsum pa gzhan lug dgag pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)005:1879: dang po sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'khor 'das tha dad du yod pa mi 'thad pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1880: de ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i ston pa kun bzang ni /
NK071(du)005:1881: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba kun dang 'das ma 'ongs da
NK071(du)005:1882: lta dus gsum gyi 'khor ba'i chosa thams cad rig
NK071(du)005:1883: pa bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub pa yin
NK071(du)005:1884: pa'i phyir / rgyal ba kun gyi phyir spyi gzugs cana yin te /
NK071(du)005:1885: de'i dgongs pa la 'khor 'das tha dad kyi cha
NK071(du)005:1886: gnyis rang rgyud can du yod par gang zag gang
NK071(du)005:1887: gi blos btags su rung ste mi rung ngo //
NK071(du)005:1888: gal te tha dad can du yod na 'khor 'das
NK071(du)005:1889: thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)005:1890: pa yin zer ba rdzun no //
NK071(du)005:1891: gnyis pa sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres pa yod pa dgag pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1892: sems tsam dang phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i 'dod tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1893: dper na nyi zera ma 'dres pa'i nyi ma'am shing
NK071(du)005:1894: gi me dpung bzhina du dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK071(du)005:1895: thams cad dgongs pa'i ngo bo kun gacaga la sbyang
NK071(du)005:1896: ba'i ye shes kyi rgyud ma 'dres so so bzhugs
NK071(du)005:1898: de ltar dgongs pa'i ye shes tha dad na sangs
NK071(du)005:1899: rgyas sprul pa yanga skur snang ba gdul bya gcig
NK071(du)005:1900: la mthun par snang ba de'ang gdul bya thams cad
NK071(du)005:1901: kun dang snang tshul gcig par 'gyur te /
NK071(du)005:1902: de'ang byang chub semas dpa' che zhes chen po 'phags
NK071(du)005:1903: pa'i snang tshul dang so so'i skye bo'i gdul bya'i
NK071(du)005:1904: snang ngor snang tshul rnams khyad mada par 'gyur ro
NK071(du)005:1905: // ye shes kyi lha rgyud tha dad na skal
NK071(du)005:1906: ldan rnams kyis lha spyan drang ba'i tshe zhi ba'i
NK071(du)005:1907: dus zhi ba'i lha tshogs rnams byon pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1908: khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams mi byon pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1909: khro bo'i dus khro bo las zhi ba mi byon pa la sogs pa'i skyon 'byung ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1912: dona gyi ngo bo dbyer med yin pa'i rgyud lung
NK071(du)005:1913: dang rigas pa man ngag gi bstan bcos kun dang
NK071(du)005:1914: 'agla ba dang / sbyangs pa'i thugs rjes 'brel ba gang yod kyi gdul bya ma gtogs pa /
NK071(du)005:1915: gdul bya gzhan gyi don du mi 'gyur basa na /
NK071(du)005:1916: rigas chada pa'i gnas su 'gyur ba'i skyon la sogs pa yod pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1917: gsum pa de drang don gyi sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK071(du)005:1918: nges don gyi sangs rgyas ma yin par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)005:1919: skyon yod pa de yi phyira sems tsam pa dang
NK071(du)005:1920: phyi rgyud kyi gang zag gang gis sangs rgyas pa'i
NK071(du)005:1921: tshe shing gi me dpung lta bur /
NK071(du)005:1922: dgongs pa'i ngo bo gcig la sbyangs pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)005:1923: ma 'dres par ston pasa de ni drang don du
NK071(du)005:1924: bkri zhing nges don du drangsa pa'i thabs kyi sangs
NK071(du)005:1925: rgyas yin pa'i phyir gsung rung gisa 'dir gsang sngags
NK071(du)005:1926: tu bkod pa'i sangs rgyas ni yanga dag par rdzogs
NK071(du)005:1927: pa ngesa para sangs rgyas mina te /
NK071(du)005:1928: de bas na thun mong dbu sems dang phyi rgyud
NK071(du)005:1929: kyi sangs rgyas pas sku lnga lhun grub tu yang
NK071(du)005:1930: dag par rdzogs pa bla na med pa'i ma h+aa'i
NK071(du)005:1931: sangas rgyas dpags pa yin no //
NK071(du)005:1932: bzhi pa rang lugs bzhag pa la gsum /
NK071(du)005:1933: dang po ye shes la yul 'dzin med cing rang
NK071(du)005:1934: snang lhun grub tu mkhyen tshul dbyer med kyi sangs
NK071(du)005:1935: rgyas de mkhyen cing gzigs pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)005:1936: dus thams cad du 'khor 'das kyi chos nyid rang
NK071(du)005:1937: rig pa kho na yin pa'i phyir gzung 'dzin gnyis
NK071(du)005:1938: su med pa la gnyis su 'dzin pa ni log
NK071(du)005:1940: log rtog de'i rgyu mtshan gyis gzung 'dzin de dag
NK071(du)005:1941: tu sna nga ba ni kun tu brtags pa te
NK071(du)005:1942: glo bur ba'o // de'i zhen pa rnam par dag
NK071(du)005:1943: pa ni bden par snang yang brtags pa yin cinga
NK071(du)005:1944: glo bur ba'o // / de ltar log rtog dag
NK071(du)005:1945: pas 'gro ba rigs drug po ril rang rig pa'i
NK071(du)005:1946: ye shes mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings lasa mi gzhan
NK071(du)005:1947: glo bur ba'o // / par gsal bas / 'gro ba thams cad ye shes des zin pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1949: gdul bya 'dul byed gnyis su mi rtog pa'i gtan tshigs gsum gyi phyir /
NK071(du)005:1950: thugsa rje skye ba'i yul dang /
NK071(du)005:1951: skye byed kyi mkhan po dang /
NK071(du)005:1952: skye ba'i thugs rje chen po dang gsum gnyis med
NK071(du)005:1953: rang snang du shar bas sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK071(du)005:1954: dang / gdul bya sems can gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig pa'i 'brel pa yod pa yisa /
NK071(du)005:1955: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med par rtogs na
NK071(du)005:1956: thugs rje chen po skyes zhes de la bya zhes
NK071(du)005:1957: so // gnyis su med pa de'i phyir 'gro ba
NK071(du)005:1958: ris drug gi dus snga phyi dang gnas mtho dman
NK071(du)005:1959: la sogs par snang ba kun lhag ma ma lus
NK071(du)005:1960: par snang zhing gsal bas na /
NK071(du)005:1961: 'gro ba mthon po mtho ris dang /
NK071(du)005:1962: damna pa ngan song gi sems can kun gyi gzugs su snang ba yang ma zad /
NK071(du)005:1963: ya ki bla na meda pa byang chub sangs rgyas kyi skur snang ba rnams kyang /
NK071(du)005:1964: dper na me long la gzugs brnyan snang ba lta
NK071(du)005:1965: bu'i tshul bzhina du sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa gnyis
NK071(du)005:1966: med rang snang gi ngang du 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)005:1967: sna tshogas pa'i kha daga ma 'dres pa dang /
NK071(du)005:1968: dbyibsa ma 'dres pa'i gzugs su snang ba'i phyi nang gi chosa rnamas ma lus pa thams cad kun /
NK071(du)005:1969: byang chub snying po'i rang bzhin sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i ye shes kyi ngang nyid du /
NK071(du)005:1970: dper na nam mkha' stong pa dang 'aja'a tshon dbyer mi phyed ba ltar /
NK071(du)005:1971: gdul bya 'dul byed ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK071(du)005:1972: par gacaga pa de yi phyir yul bral gnyis meda
NK071(du)005:1973: du shes bya thams cada mkhyen pa'o //
NK071(du)005:1974: gnyis pa thugs rje chen po'i ngang du phrin las
NK071(du)005:1975: byed bsam gyi rtog pa med cing gdul bya'i re
NK071(du)005:1976: ba skong ba la dgongs pa la 'gro 'ong med
NK071(du)005:1977: par gzugs sna tshogs su snang nas rang dang mthun
NK071(du)005:1979: dper na dapaga bsam ljon shing dang yid bzhin nor
NK071(du)005:1980: bu rin chen las dgos 'dod sna tshogs 'byung yang
NK071(du)005:1982: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yul yul can gyi rtog
NK071(du)005:1983: pa mada para yul bral gnyis med kyi ngang nas
NK071(du)005:1984: gdul bya gang la gang 'dul gyi gzugs su snang
NK071(du)005:1985: nas re ba skong ba dang /
NK071(du)005:1986: de la chu dwangs pa'i nang du 'gro 'ong med
NK071(du)005:1987: par nyi zla chu la snang ba ltar dang me
NK071(du)005:1988: long du gzugs brnyan 'char ba ltar sangs rgyas kyi
NK071(du)005:1989: dgongs pa la 'gro 'ong med par gdul bya nye
NK071(du)005:1990: ring med pa kun la gzugs sku sna tshogs su
NK071(du)005:1991: snang ba'i sku zhi khro la sogs ba dang gsung
NK071(du)005:1993: thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang mngon shes kyi bye
NK071(du)005:1994: brag la sogs pa chosa sgo sna tshogs kyis gdul
NK071(du)005:1995: bya la ji ltar rang rang gi blo dang 'atshamas
NK071(du)005:1996: par sems can gyi rgyud yongs su 'grol bar byed
NK071(du)005:1997: pa'i mdzad pa'o // gsum pa thugs rje la nye
NK071(du)005:1998: ring med cing 'gro don la sems par rgyun du
NK071(du)005:2000: de ltar bu'i thugs spros pa dang bral zhing thugs
NK071(du)005:2001: rjes bgos pa med par 'gro ba yongs la khyab
NK071(du)005:2002: pa'i semas la 'du 'bral med cing nar sona bas
NK071(du)005:2003: na 'das ma 'ongs da lnga'i dus gsum gyi gnas
NK071(du)005:2004: skabs kun la phyogs ris med par snyomsa par zhugsa
NK071(du)005:2005: pa'o // mtha' mar dge ba mjug gi don la gnyis te /
NK071(du)005:2006: dgos ched dang bsngo ba smon lam /
NK071(du)005:2007: mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan gnyis las /
NK071(du)005:2009: 'gro ba sems can gyi nang nas lam log ba mu stegs rtag chad yin no //
NK071(du)005:2010: de yang snang phyogs la zhen cing log pa rtag lta ba dang /
NK071(du)005:2011: stong phyogs la zhen cing log pa chad lta ba'o //
NK071(du)005:2012: lam stor ba ni so so'i skye bo tha mal pa rnams dang /
NK071(du)005:2013: de dag gis gsang sngags zung 'jug gi lam la mi 'jug cinga /
NK071(du)005:2014: shes rab kyis dbang po sgo lnga gnyis med rang
NK071(du)005:2015: snang du snang srid dag mnyam chen por rtogs pa'i
NK071(du)005:2016: rkyen rdo rje slob dpon dang thos bsam bsgom pa
NK071(du)005:2017: sogs kyi yon tan dang bral zhing sngar gyi bag
NK071(du)005:2018: chags rnam rtog ma rig 'khor ba'i gcong nad kyis
NK071(du)005:2019: snying la mi bzod pa'i sdug bsngal dag gis zin
NK071(du)005:2020: pa rnams kyi don bya ba'i phyir 'bras bu sgrub
NK071(du)005:2021: thabs kyi lam / nye ba bde ba rjogs pas na mchoga /
NK071(du)005:2022: dug gsum gyi nad sel ba'i bdud rtsi yi sman chen po 'di nyid /
NK071(du)005:2023: rgyud nas 'thor ba rnams slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang
NK071(du)005:2024: bas bsdus pa yi dge ba'i rtsa ba des mtha'
NK071(du)005:2025: yas pa'i sems can rnams kyis lam 'grod nas rgyal
NK071(du)005:2026: ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par
NK071(du)005:2027: shog cig ces bsngo ba smon lam gdab bo //
NK071(du)005:2028: gnyis pa brtsam pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK071(du)005:2029: dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po gsang
NK071(du)005:2030: ba snying po nyams su len pa rnams kyi lam
NK071(du)005:2031: gyi rim pa rnam par bshad pa tshig tshogs nyung
NK071(du)005:2032: ngu'am chung ngu ru bsdus pa zhes bya ba 'di
NK071(du)005:2033: nyid slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang basa rgyud
NK071(du)005:2034: 'bum phrag brgya ba'i don bsdus te mdzad pa tshig
NK071(du)005:2035: don ma lus pa grub pas na rdzagas so zhes
NK071(du)005:2036: so // rgya gar 'phags yul mkhas grub rgyu skar dbus //
NK071(du)005:2037: nyi ma lta bu rgyal ba gnyis pa zhes //
NK071(du)005:2038: yongs basngagasa slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba yis //
NK071(du)005:2039: tan+t+ra bco brgyad la sogs stong phrag brgya'i //
NK071(du)005:2040: gdams ngag bcud bsdus lam rim chung ngu 'di //
NK071(du)005:2041: rig 'dzin bye ba'i gshegs shul rmad byung chos //
NK071(du)005:2042: rnam mkhyen thob 'dod kun gyi snying nor zung //
NK071(du)005:2043: rgyud don zab rgyas gting dpag gzhal dka' rnams //
NK071(du)005:2044: 'phrad daka'i chos mchog 'di yis legs par rtogs //
NK071(du)005:2045: de phyir thos bsam bsgom la brtson par mdzod //
NK071(du)005:2046: rang ngos 'chad dang rtsom pa'i yon tan med //
NK071(du)005:2047: gzhan don 'byung ba'i bsam pa bdag la med //
NK071(du)005:2048: ci phyir zhe na da lta snyigs dus 'dir //
NK071(du)005:2049: nyams su len pa nyin skar tsam du zad //
NK071(du)005:2050: 'on kyang chos 'di'i 'grel bshad nub nye tshe //
NK071(du)005:2051: sems kyis ma bzod tshig 'grel mdor bsdus 'di //
NK071(du)005:2052: nyin gsum ngal dub spangs nas mthar phyin du //
